0for%20now%2C%20having%20a%20dog%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20flexibility%20of%20DINKdom%20%E2%80%94%20has%20meant%20emotional%20support%20and%20bandwidth.%20Having%20a%20child%20right%20now%20would%20mean%20having%20to%20explain%20the%20situation%20to%20them%2C%20something%20that%20would%20be%20very%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20cry%20myself%20to%20sleep%20sometimes%2C%20and%20I've%20got%20her%20to%20cuddle%20with%20and%20she's%20this%20big%20fluffy%20dog.%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20I'd%20be%20able%20to%20do%20that%20with%20a%20kid%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'd%20be%20emotionally%20supporting%20it%20and%20teaching%20it%20everything%20about%20the%20world%2C%20and%20the%20current%20situation%2C%20and%20it'd%20be%20totally%20different.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-dink-dinkwad-grateful-childfree-lifestyle-right-now-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706439421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b2a8b26c8f0a134f7a0a8b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-dink-dinkwad-grateful-childfree-lifestyle-right-now-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Being%20a%20DINK%20is%20more%20than%20just%20the%20freedom%20to%20travel%20and%20spend.%20It%20also%20means%20a%20safety%20net%20and%20less%20stress%20during%20hard%20times.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Juliana%20Kaplan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-dink-dinkwad-grateful-childfree-lifestyle-right-now-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22For%20the%20ICJ%20to%20Say%20It%20Is%20'Plausible'%20That%20Israel%20Is%20Carrying%20Out%20Genocide%20Is%20a%20Defining%20Moment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F28140819%2FGEw1UHwXMAEPdVM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20case%20charging%20Israel%20with%20genocide%2C%20in%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Ficj-says-israel-must-comply-with-genocide-convention-but-stops-short-of-halting-military-operation%5C%22%3Eprovisional%20measures%20were%20announced%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20January%2026%2C%20is%20a%20marker%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20conflict%20raging%20currently%2C%20and%20posits%20a%20moral%20prism%20to%20view%20the%20competing%20narratives.%20Raphael%20Lemkin%2C%20a%20legal%20scholar%20and%20a%20World%20War%20II%20refugee%20from%20Western%20Ukraine%20who%20lost%20considerable%20family%20in%20the%20Shoah%2C%20is%20widely%20considered%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20Genocide%20Convention%2C%20which%20was%20a%20direct%20reaction%20to%20the%20Holocaust.%20Legal%20defences%20aside%2C%20that%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%2C%20a%20state%20sanctioned%20largely%20by%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20shame%20over%20allowing%20the%20Nazi%20Holocaust%20to%20occur%2C%20today%20faces%20a%20credible%20charge%20of%20genocide%20is%20a%20tragic%20irony%20of%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELemkin%20spent%20much%20of%20the%20war%20studying%20Nazi%20documents%20and%20ordinances%20to%20analyse%20the%20motive%20underlying%20Nazi%20repression%20and%20massacres%2C%20which%20today%20we%20understand%20to%20be%20archetypically%20genocidal%2C%20including%20implementing%20%3Cem%3ELebensraum%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20colonial%20stratagem%20previously%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fsurviving-genocide-colonial-namibia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemployed%20by%20the%20Germans%20in%20Namibia%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20used%20to%20depopulate%20territories%20for%20settling%20Germans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20the%20seemingly%20indiscriminate%20killings%20of%20civilians%20in%20Gaza%20by%20Israeli%20bombardment%2C%20which%20may%20be%20a%20war%20crime%20in%20itself%2C%20but%20the%20motive%20behind%20it%20which%20is%20called%20into%20question%20in%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20case.%20Lemkin%20in%20his%20writing%20explained%20that%20genocide%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.preventgenocide.org%2Flemkin%2Ffreeworld1945.htm%5C%22%3Erefers%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20plan%20%E2%80%9Caimed%20at%20destruction%20of%20the%20essential%20foundations%20of%20the%20life%20of%20national%20groups%20so%20that%20these%20groups%20wither%20and%20die%20like%20plants%20that%20have%20suffered%20a%20blight%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FLemkinInstitute%2Fstatus%2F1714599755609718970%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELemkin%20Institute%20for%20Genocide%20Prevention%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20now%20deleted%20post%20by%20the%20%40IsraelPM%20X%20handle%20%E2%80%9Cis%20an%20expression%20of%20genodical%20intent%E2%80%9D%2C%20in%20which%20it%20was%20written%20%E2%80%9C%5Bt%5Dhis%20is%20a%20struggle%20between%20the%20children%20of%20the%20light%20and%20the%20children%20of%20darkness%2C%20between%20humanity%20and%20the%20law%20of%20the%20jungle%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20lots%20of%20other%20statements%20too%20and%20the%20question%20sought%20to%20be%20answered%20in%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20case%20is%20whether%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20Israeli%20military%20campaign%20itself%2C%20and%2For%20the%20public%20declarations%20of%20collective%20punishment%2C%20and%2For%20the%20cutting%20off%20of%20water%2C%20food%20and%20fuel%20supplies%2C%20were%20sufficient%20for%20the%20court%20to%20prescribe%20emergency%20interim%20measures%20that%20Israel%20must%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20attacks%20on%20Palestinians%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20often%20by%20or%20in%20aid%20of%20Israeli%20settlers%2C%20also%20raises%20concerns%20on%20genocidal%20intent.%20For%20its%20parts%2C%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20arguments%20in%20the%20ICJ%20did%20not%20link%20the%20settlement%20policies%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20to%20the%20situation%20in%20Gaza.%20The%20ICJ%20is%20considering%20a%20separate%20advisory%20opinion%20on%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icj-cij.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fcase-related%2F186%2F186-20231114-pre-01-00-en.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20policies%20and%20practices%20of%20Israel%20in%20the%20Occupied%20Palestinian%20Territories%2C%20including%20East%20Jerusalem%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icj-cij.org%2Fhome%5C%22%3Epreliminary%20ruling%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20January%2026%2C%20the%20ICJ%20found%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20case%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cplausible%E2%80%9D%2C%20or%20sufficiently%20%3Cem%3Eprima%20facie%20%3C%2Fem%3Efor%20it%20to%20direct%20provisional%20measures.%20Israel%20%E2%80%93%20which%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20has%20said%20was%20set%20up%20to%20ensure%20that%20a%20Holocaust%20%E2%80%9Cnever%20again%E2%80%9D%20happens%20%E2%80%93%20is%20prime%20facie%20indicated%20to%20be%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20Genocide%20Convention.%20The%20ICJ%20took%20note%20of%20the%20conduct%20of%20Israeli%20forces%2C%20statements%20of%20UN%20officials%20and%20Israeli%20officials%2C%20and%20the%20situation%20in%20Gaza%20in%20itself.%20It%20also%20took%20note%20of%20the%20UN%E2%80%99s%20Committee%20on%20the%20Elimination%20of%20Racial%20Discrimination%20which%20found%20%E2%80%9Cracist%20hate%20speech%E2%80%9D%20and%20an%20expert%20group%E2%80%99s%20report%20that%20found%20%E2%80%9Cdiscernibly%20genocidal%20and%20dehumanising%20rhetoric%E2%80%9D.%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20self-declared%20steps%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20Genocide%20Convention%20were%20held%20to%20be%20insufficient%20to%20remove%20the%20risk%20of%20%E2%80%9Cirreparable%20prejudice%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20under%20the%20Genocide%20Convention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22By%20Invoking%20Genocide%20Convention%2C%20ICJ%20Makes%20It%20Clear%20Israel's%20Killing%20of%20Palestinians%20is%20Not%20'War'%20But%20Crime%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fby-invoking-genocide-convention-icj-makes-it-clear-israels-killing-of-palestinians-is-not-war-but-crime%5C%22%3EBy%20Invoking%20Genocide%20Convention%2C%20ICJ%20Makes%20It%20Clear%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20Killing%20of%20Palestinians%20is%20Not%20%E2%80%98War%E2%80%99%20But%20Crime%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icj-cij.org%2Fnode%2F203452%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseparate%20opinion%20as%20judge%20ad%20joc%20appointed%20by%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20and%20not%2C%20as%20he%20emphatically%20notes%2C%20its%20agent%20%E2%80%93%20Aharon%20Barak%2C%20a%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20Israeli%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20has%20anguish%20seeping%20through%20his%20words.%20He%20evokes%20the%20memory%20of%20Lemkin.%20Barak%20was%20a%20five%20year%20old%20when%20Nazis%20put%20him%20with%20his%20family%20in%20a%20ghetto%2C%20and%20he%20is%20himself%20a%20survivor%20of%20the%20genocide%20in%20Lithuania.%20He%20writes%20that%20%E2%80%9C%5Bg%5Denocide%20is%20more%20than%20a%20word%20for%20me%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Cidea%20that%20Israel%20is%20now%20accused%20of%20committing%20genocide%20is%20very%20hard%20for%20me%20personally%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20His%20statement%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cevery%20Israeli%20soldier%20carries%20with%20him%20(or%20her)%20in%20their%20backpack%2C%20the%20rules%20of%20international%20law%E2%80%9D%20will%20jar%20those%20watching%20the%20bombardment%20live.%20However%2C%20even%20though%20Barak%20finds%20no%20plausible%20links%20to%20genocidal%20intent%2C%20he%20struggles%20with%20the%20situation%20and%20votes%20for%20humanitarian%20aid%20and%20the%20direction%20to%20stop%20incitement%20to%20genocide%20%E2%80%93%20the%20latter%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdecrease%20tensions%20and%20discourage%20damaging%20rhetoric%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20make%20or%20break%20moment%20in%20international%20law.%20Although%20no%20state%20has%20formally%20joined%20the%20case%20with%20South%20Africa%2C%20the%20divide%20in%20those%20indicating%20support%20and%20those%20against%20runs%20through%20a%20global%20north-south%20divide.%20Of%20the%20BRICS%20countries%2C%20Brazil%20has%20supported%20South%20Africa%20explicitly%2C%20and%20Russia%20and%20China%20have%20been%20sympathetic.%20India%20has%20been%20silent%20on%20the%20case.%20The%20global%20north%20has%20come%20out%20against%20the%20case%20itself%2C%20and%20as%20traditional%20exponents%20of%20what%20they%20call%20the%20international%20%E2%80%98rules-based%20order%E2%80%99%2C%20countries%20such%20as%20Germany%2C%20which%20has%20referred%20to%20the%20historical%20necessity%20to%20support%20Israel%2C%20are%20faced%20with%20difficult%20choices.%20Canada%20has%20been%20another%20vocal%20supporter%20of%20Israeli%20actions%2C%20in%20contrast%20to%20its%20oft%20stated%20position%20as%20a%20stronger%20supporter%20of%20international%20law.%20However%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eeas.europa.eu%2Feeas%2Ficj-joint-statement-high-representative-and-european-commission_en%5C%22%3EEU%20Commission%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20quick%20to%20announce%20after%20the%20order%20that%20ICJ%20judgments%20are%20binding%20and%20it%20expects%20compliance.%20This%20can%20only%20lead%20to%20a%20churn%20in%20the%20international%20system%2C%20and%20a%20shift%20towards%20more%20%3Cem%3Ereal%20politik%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20a%20passing%20of%20some%20of%20the%20power%20enjoyed%20by%20traditional%20exponents.%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20bringing%20the%20case%20is%20in%20itself%20indicative%20of%20that%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20bringing%20the%20case%2C%20South%20Africa%20is%20not%20just%20exercising%20its%20legal%20right%20as%20a%20signatory%20to%20the%20Genocide%20Convention%2C%20but%20also%20discharging%20an%20obligation%20flowing%20from%20the%20moral%20authority%20of%20Nelson%20Mandela%2C%20who%20was%20an%20ardent%20supporter%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%2C%20and%20considered%20himself%20in%20solidarity%20with%2C%20and%20in%20debt%20to%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20leadership%20for%20its%20support%20of%20the%20African%20National%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20struggle%20against%20apartheid.%20Consistent%20with%20this%20history%20was%20Israel%20and%20Apartheid%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Ereal%20politik%20%3C%2Fem%3Emutual%20support.%20There%20are%20also%20suggestions%20that%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20case%20is%20due%20to%20the%20need%20to%20shore%20up%20domestic%20support%20for%20President%20Cyril%20Ramaphosa%2C%20but%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20argue%20that%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20motives%20are%20strictly%20cynical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20bring%20a%20case%20was%20a%20particularly%20Lemkinesque%20insertion%20into%20the%20Genocide%20Convention%2C%20which%20made%20the%20crime%20of%20genocide%20a%20crime%20against%20all%20humanity%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3Ehostis%20generis%20humani%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%93%20thereby%20making%20it%C2%A0the%20duty%20of%20every%20country%20to%20prevent%20such%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22What%20Explains%20the%20Desensitisation%20of%20the%20Western%20Leadership%20Towards%20Horrors%20in%20Gaza%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwhat-explains-the-desensitisation-of-the-western-leadership-towards-horrors-in-gaza%5C%22%3EWhat%20Explains%20the%20Desensitisation%20of%20the%20Western%20Leadership%20Towards%20Horrors%20in%20Gaza%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20been%20ordered%20to%20not%20carry%20out%20genocide%2C%20to%20disallow%20and%20prosecute%20the%20public%20and%20direct%20incitement%20to%20genocide%2C%20to%20allow%20humanitarian%20aid%2C%20and%20to%20report%20to%20the%20court%20with%20a%20copy%20to%20South%20Africa%20within%2030%20days.%20The%20court%20has%20no%20sheriff%20it%20can%20send%20to%20coerce%20compliance%2C%20but%20is%20a%20moral%20expression%20of%20international%20law%3B%20Israel%20and%20its%20supporters%20will%20find%20their%20arguments%20harder%20to%20make%20now%20that%20the%20ICJ%20has%20said%20there%20is%20a%20%3Cem%3Eprima%20facie%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecase%20of%20genocide%20they%20are%20answerable%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20State%20now%20faces%20a%20choice%20%E2%80%93%20probably%20being%20articulated%20by%20many%20of%20its%20supporters%20%E2%80%93%20of%20hunkering%20down%20into%20an%20us-versus-the-rest-of-the-world%20mindset%2C%20and%20accusing%20the%20court%20of%20being%20a%20backer%20of%20terror%2C%20or%20of%20travelling%2C%20or%20be%20forced%20to%20travel%2C%20down%20the%20hard%20path%20to%20a%20re-think.%20The%20early%20signs%20are%20not%20encouraging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAvi%20Singh%20is%20an%20advocate%20who%20specialises%20in%20transnational%20and%20international%20law%20and%20is%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20International%20University%20College%2C%20Turin.%20He%20has%20also%20practiced%20before%20international%20criminal%20tribunals.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706439207000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F28140819%2FGEw1UHwXMAEPdVM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Ffor-the-icj-to-say-it-is-plausible-that-israel-is-carrying-out-genocide-is-a-defining-moment%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22That%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%2C%20a%20state%20sanctioned%20largely%20by%20the%20world's%20shame%20over%20allowing%20the%20Nazi%20Holocaust%20to%20occur%2C%20today%20faces%20a%20credible%20charge%20of%20genocide%20is%20a%20tragic%20irony%20of%20history.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%2