r%20people%20is%20far%20too%20prevalent.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20started%20a%20free%20group%20at%20his%20local%20senior%20center%2C%20where%20residents%20can%20gather%20and%20simply%20talk.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20happiness%2C%20Lamy%20said%2C%20it's%20not%20about%20money%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20about%20relationships.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJoe%20Lamy%2C%2075%2C%20recently%20went%20to%20the%20Walgreens%20pharmacy%20in%20Seattle%20where%20he%20watched%20the%20pharmacist%20sift%20pills%20into%20various%20containers%20as%20he%20waited%20patiently%20in%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20his%20turn%20finally%20came%20to%20approach%20the%20counter%2C%20the%20pharmacist%20placed%20a%20pill%20bottle%20into%20a%20bag%2C%20stapled%20it%2C%20and%20tossed%20it%20into%20a%20box%20about%20eight%20feet%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGood%20shot%2C%26quot%3B%20Lamy%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid%20to%20the%20pharamist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPractice%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20replied%2C%20and%20each%20of%20them%20carried%20on%20with%20their%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20interaction%20might%20have%20been%20insignificant%20to%20the%20pharmacist%2C%20it%20carried%20meaning%20for%20Lamy%20and%20shifted%20the%20course%20of%20his%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20have%20to%20say%20anything%2C%20but%20I%20did%2C%26quot%3B%20Lamy%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it%20made%20me%20happy.%20She%20and%20I%20had%20this%20little%20moment%2C%20this%20tiny%20little%20moment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22707%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joe%20Lamy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b1444943bb77284ba03445%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22530%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoe%20Lamy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20tiny%20moments%20signify%20the%20importance%20of%20what%20a%20Johns%20Hopkins%202015%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cs.umd.edu%2F~golbeck%2FINST633o%2FgranovetterTies.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearch%20paper%3C%2Fa%3E%20coined%20as%20%26quot%3Bweak%20ties%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20the%20New%20York%20Times%20previously%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Blow-stakes%20relationships%26quot%3B%20that%20help%20people%20feel%20more%20connected%20to%20others%20that%20they%20might%20not%20know%20very%20well.%20A%202014%20psychology%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1177%2F0146167214529799%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20weak%20ties%20help%20make%20people%20happier%20and%20spark%20an%20increased%20sense%20of%20belonging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20retiree%20living%20on%20Social%20Security%20and%20some%20financial%20help%20from%20his%20family%2C%20Lamy%20said%20he's%20grown%20to%20value%20the%20small%20interactions%20he%20has%20with%20people%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20given%20the%20loneliness%20epidemic%20that's%20hitting%20some%20seniors%20especially%20hard.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthyagingpoll.org%2Freports-more%2Freport%2Ftrends-loneliness-among-older-adults-2018-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20University%20of%20Michigan%20National%20Poll%20on%20Healthy%20Aging%2C%20a%20January%202023%20survey%20of%202%2C563%20adults%20aged%2050%20to%2080%20found%20that%20one%20in%20three%20adults%20reported%20feeling%20isolated%2C%20and%2037%25%20of%20them%20reported%20feeling%20a%20lack%20of%20companionship%20in%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESurgeon%20General%20Vivek%20Murthy%20also%20addressed%20the%20loneliness%20crisis%20over%20the%20past%20and%20laid%20out%20a%20framework%20to%20help%20address%20it%2C%20saying%20in%20a%20previous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hhs.gov%2Fabout%2Fnews%2F2023%2F05%2F03%2Fnew-surgeon-general-advisory-raises-alarm-about-devastating-impact-epidemic-loneliness-isolation-united-states.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%26quot%3Bour%20epidemic%20of%20loneliness%20and%20isolation%20has%20been%20an%20underappreciated%20public%20health%20crisis%20that%20has%20harmed%20individual%20and%20societal%20health.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20relationships%20are%20a%20source%20of%20healing%20and%20well-being%20hiding%20in%20plain%20sight%20%E2%80%93%20one%20that%20can%20help%20us%20live%20healthier%2C%20more%20fulfilled%2C%20and%20more%20productive%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20loneliness%20among%20older%20adults%20prompted%20Lamy%20to%20take%20a%20second%20look%20at%20what%20he%20prioritizes%20in%20life%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20found%20that%20money%20and%20wealth%20are%20low%20on%20the%20list%2C%20while%20social%20interactions%20are%20up%20top.%20About%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20he%20started%20a%20group%20at%20a%20senior%20center%20in%20Seattle%20where%20residents%20can%20simply%20gather%20together%20in%20a%20room%20and%20talk%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20changed%20his%20outlook%20on%20life%2C%20and%20he's%20much%20happier%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20little%20moments%20that%20are%20actually%20more%20important%20in%20our%20joy%20than%20making%2020%20bucks%2C%26quot%3B%20Lamy%20said.%20%26quot%3BNot%20that%20money's%20not%20important.%20It%20just%20doesn't%20fill%20you%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'It's%20a%20lifesaver'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELamy%20said%20he%20never%20made%20much%20money%20throughout%20his%20life.%20Before%20becoming%20an%20English%20teacher%20%E2%80%94%20the%20job%20he%20had%20up%20until%20his%20retirement%20in%202021%20%E2%80%94%20he%20installed%20insulation%20in%20the%20homes%20of%20low-income%20and%20older%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20found%20that%20upon%20retirement%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20his%20daily%20social%20interactions%20dwindled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20big%20thing%20that%20happens%20when%20you%20get%20older%20is%20your%20friends%20leave%2C%20your%20spouse%20dies%2C%20or%20your%20neighbors%20that%20you%20trusted%20move%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Lamy%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20you%20don't%20have%20your%20job%20anymore%2C%20and%20to%20me%2C%20that%20cuts%20off%20a%20huge%20flow%20of%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20no%20longer%20has%20that%20issue.%20As%20a%20facilitator%20of%20the%20biweekly%20meetings%20at%20the%20senior%20center%2C%20Lamy%20said%20he%20usually%20begins%20each%20session%20with%20a%20discussion%20topic%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20often%20evolves%20into%20a%20flowing%20conversation%20that%20can%20last%20hours%20beyond%20the%20one-hour%20allotted%20time%20for%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20had%20our%20first%20meeting%2C%20I%20asked%20them%2C%20'How%20many%20of%20you%20have%20people%20you%20can%20talk%20to%3F'%20And%20only%20half%20the%20people%20raised%20their%20hand%2C%26quot%3B%20Lamy%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20said%2C%20'Do%20you%20mean%20to%20tell%20me%20that%20four%20of%20you%20don't%20have%20any%20person%20you%20can%20talk%20to%20in%20your%20life%20about%20anything%3F'%20And%20they%20said%2C%20'Yes%2C%20that's%20why%20we're%20here.'%20And%20it%20just%20broke%20my%20heart.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Lamy%20is%20working%20with%20AARP%2C%20formerly%20the%20American%20Association%20of%20Retired%20Persons%2C%20to%20recruit%20facilitators%20to%20hold%20groups%20nationwide%20and%20give%20older%20people%20a%20free%20option%20to%20combat%20loneliness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Business%20Insider%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-loneliness-does-to-the-body-and-brain-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20loneliness%20can%20have%20significant%20impacts%20on%20people's%20mental%20and%20physical%20well-being.%20Over%20time%2C%20loneliness%20can%20damage%20a%20person's%20sleep%20schedule%2C%20immune%20system%2C%20heart%20health%2C%20and%20memory%20if%20the%20issue%20isn't%20reversed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20implications%20become%20that%20dire%2C%20Lamy%20said%2C%20the%20typical%20American%20Dream%20concerns%2C%20like%20being%20successful%20and%20accumulating%20wealth%2C%20are%20not%20important.%20Relationships%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20comes%20down%20to%20simple%20empathy%20and%20realizing%20that%20people%20really%20do%20need%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Lamy%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20when%20you%20reach%20out%20and%20take%20the%20initiative%20to%20help%20someone%20who%20is%20in%20need%2C%20it%20sort%20of%20opened%20them%20up%20to%20begin%20to%20trust.%20It's%20a%20lifesaver.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floneliness-crisis-retiree-how-to-achieve-happiness-budget-retirement-seniors-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706437621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b143d543bb77284ba0340f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floneliness-crisis-retiree-how-to-achieve-happiness-budget-retirement-seniors-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Joe%20Lamy%20is%20surviving%20on%20Social%20Security%2C%20but%20his%20focus%20isn't%20on%20money.%20It's%20on%20the%20loneliness%20epidemic%2C%20and%20he%20thinks%20he%20might've%20found%20a%20solution.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floneliness-crisis-retiree-how-to-achieve-happiness-budget-retirement-seniors-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20to%20assist%20in%20rescue%20of%20Sri%20Lanka%20fishermen%20captured%20by%20Somali%20pirates%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706437153000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107203670%2Cimgsize-32682.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2