0the%20alliance%20pointing%20to%20corruption%20charges%20against%20then%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20and%20his%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20wouldn't%20be%20right%20if%20I%20didn't%20take%20a%20stand%2C%20I%20don't%20do%20politics%20of%20this%20kind.%20I%20felt%20suffocated%2C%20my%20conscience%20pricked%20me.%20there%20was%20no%20other%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kumar%2C%20once%20known%20for%20his%20clean%20image%2C%20had%20then%20told%20the%20media.%20In%20another%20statement%2C%20in%20which%20he%20did%20not%20name%20any%20party%20but%20was%20apparently%20targeting%20RJD%2C%20he%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMany%20JD(U)%20MLAs%20were%20being%20lured%20to%20defect%20from%20the%20party.%20My%20MLAs%20refused%20all%20allurements%20and%20told%20me%20who%20came%20with%20huge%20offers%20to%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2013%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar's%202013%20exit%20from%20the%20NDA%2C%20after%20a%2017-year-old%20alliance%2C%20was%20the%20first%20in%20his%20series%20of%20flip-flops.%20The%20bone%20of%20contention%20then%20was%20the%20BJP's%20choice%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20as%20its%20face%20for%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20parting%20ways%20from%20the%20NDA%20is%20the%20BJP's%20failure.%20You%20created%20a%20situation%20in%20which%20the%20old%20allies%20walked%20away.%20An%20alliance%20does%20not%20run%20under%20compulsion.%20If%20any%20party%20wants%20to%20form%20a%20government%2C%20the%20responsibility%20is%20of%20that%20party%20to%20get%20the%20support%20of%20other%20parties%20if%20it%20is%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20get%20the%20numbers%20for%20it%20on%20its%20own.%20And%20here%20an%20old%20ally%20was%20forced%20to%20leave%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kumar%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706436660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fo58430eo_nitish-kumar-ani_625x300_28_January_24.jpg