2%3EBalance%20the%20Grind%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20then%20does%2015%20minutes%20of%20stretching%20and%20a%2030-minute%20run%20no%20matter%20where%20he%20is%20or%20how%20little%20sleep%20he's%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20leaves%20work%20at%20the%20office%2C%20walking%20out%20the%20door%20about%205%20p.m.%20and%20spends%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20day%20with%20his%20family.%20Nadella's%20also%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tbsnews.net%2Fworld%2Fpeople-should-not-reply-late-night-emails-work-after-shift-timing-says-microsoft-ceo-satya%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0encouraged%3C%2Fa%3E%20workers%20not%20to%20answer%20emails%20on%20weekends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20be%20engaged%20in%20conversations%20and%20do%20deep%20work%2C%20rather%20than%20over-scheduling%20and%20adding%20more%20burden%20to%20feel%20like%20I'm%20productive%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mensjournal.com%2Fentertainment%2Fmicrosoft-ceo-satya-nadella-advice%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMen's%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20decade%20as%20CEO%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Microsoft%20CEO%20Satya%20Nadella%20speaks%20to%20guests%20at%20an%20Economic%20Club%20of%20Chicago%20dinner%20on%20October%203%2C%202018%20in%20Chicago%2C%20Illinois.%20Nadella%20succeeded%20Steve%20Ballmer%20as%20Microsoft%20CEO%20in%202014.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b2301e6c8f0a134f79e830%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EScott%20Olson%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Nadella%20took%20home%20just%20under%20%2448.5%20million%2C%20with%20%242.5%20million%20from%20salary%20and%20almost%20%2440%20million%20in%20stock.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%20Nadella%20owned%20more%20than%201.5%20million%20shares%20in%20Mic