rds%20away%20from%20a%20trailer%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20main%20supercenters%20in%20my%20area%3A%20Walmart%20store%20No.%205260%2C%20which%20is%20south%20of%20town%20on%20Pleasant%20Crossing%20Boulevard%2C%20and%20Walmart%20store%20No.%201%2C%20which%20is%20located%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20Rogers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPleasant%20Crossing%20is%20near%20the%20rich%20part%20of%20town%2C%20while%20the%20Rogers%20store%20is%20located%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20old%20downtown%20Rogers%2C%20closer%20to%20the%20nursing%20homes%20and%20apartment%20complexes.%20It's%20not%20the%20worst%20part%20of%20town%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20not%20exactly%20the%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20I'll%20try%20anything%20I%20can%20to%20stick%20to%20the%20store%20downtown%2C%20because%20I%20know%20I'm%20going%20to%20end%20up%20with%20better%20tips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20same%20thing%20when%20you%20talk%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstacart-doordash-uber-federal-rule-wont-change-gig-workers-status-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eother%20types%20of%20delivery%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20area.%20Whether%20they%20deliver%20pizzas%20or%20drive%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoordash-history-milestones-food-delivery-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDoorDash%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20they'll%20tell%20you%20the%20same%20thing%3A%20We'd%20rather%20stay%20close%20to%20the%20hood%20and%20near%20the%20bars%2C%20because%20we%20know%20we're%20going%20to%20get%20better%20tips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20experiences%20leave%20me%20disappointed%2C%20but%20not%20surprised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20here%2C%20and%20I've%20experienced%20living%20at%20many%20economic%20levels%20in%20northwest%20Arkansas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20I%20was%20living%20with%20my%20parents%20when%20I%20was%20younger%2C%20working%20at%20a%20great-paying%20corporate%20gig%2C%20or%20being%20a%20single%20parent%2C%20I've%20had%20my%20share%20of%20financial%20ups%20and%20downs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-first-trillionaire-minted-10-years-richest-oxfam-musk-bezos-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20major%20disconnect%20in%20this%20country%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20how%20we%20value%20time%20based%20on%20our%20present%20position%20in%20society%2C%20and%20how%20we%20value%20other%20people's%20time%20based%20on%20their%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20going%20to%20say%20those%20people%20living%20in%20the%20gated%20community%20don't%20deserve%20to%20be%20in%20that%20gated%20community.%20Whether%20it's%20by%20virtue%20of%20birth%20or%20hard%20work%2C%20they're%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20to%20forget%20what%20it's%20like%20to%20not%20live%20in%20that%20gated%20community%20%E2%80%94%20to%20forget%20or%20not%20even%20understand%20because%20you've%20had%20access%20to%20wealth%20for%20multiple%20generations%20%E2%80%94%20to%20not%20know%20what%20it's%20like%20to%20rely%20on%20tip%20income%20to%20survive%20and%20to%20protect%20and%20provide%20for%20your%20family%20is%20just%20disheartening%20to%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20conversation%20about%20how%20people%20who%20are%20in%20positions%20of%20economic%20power%20view%20and%20value%20those%20who%20aren't%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20they%20rely%20on%20our%20labor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20think%20I%20should%20be%20paid%20a%20fair%20wage%20and%20shouldn't%20rely%20on%20tips%2C%20don't%20use%20services%20that%20require%20me%20to%20not%20have%20a%20fair%20wage%20and%20to%20rely%20on%20tips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20time%20I%20use%20DoorDash%20or%20Spark%20is%20when%20I%20can%20afford%20a%20reasonable%20tip.%20I%20know%20the%20drivers%20get%20paid%20a%20certain%20amount%20from%20the%20store%2C%20and%20whenever%20I%20tip%2C%20I%20assume%20I'm%20the%20only%20order%20they'll%20have%20for%20that%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20try%20to