emain%20relevant%20as%20an%20institution%20needs%20recognising%20challenges%20and%20starting%20difficult%20conversations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20digital%20Supreme%20Court%20reports%20will%20make%20judgments%20available%20to%20people%20for%20free%20in%20a%20digital%20format.%20All%20519%20volumes%20of%20Supreme%20Court%20reports%20since%201950%2C%20covering%2036%2C308%20cases%2C%20will%20be%20available%20in%20digital%20format%2C%20bookmarked%2C%20user-friendly%20and%20with%20open%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20inaugurated%20the%20celebrations%20today.%20A%20new%20website%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20also%20launched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20is%20a%20momentous%20occasion...%20It%20was%20through%20the%20Constitution%20that%20people%20gave%20it%20to%20themselves%20this%20court.%20The%20Constitution%20is%20about%20mutual%20respect%20towards%20fellow%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said%20in%20his%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20held%20its%20inaugural%20sitting%20on%20January%2028%2C%201950.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20the%20future...%20We%20are%20also%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20opening%20a%20war%20room%20equipped%20with%20technology%20enabling%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20monitor%20real-time%20judicial%20data%20of%20the%20entire%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B1.23%20lakh%20passes%20have%20been%20generated%20digitally%20using%20Suswagatam.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20move%20all%20its%20files%20to%20a%20safe%20and%20sovereign%20cloud-based%20infrastructure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuswagatam%20is%20an%20online%20app%20that%20allows%20users%20to%20register%20and%20request%20e-passes%20to%20attend%20court%20proceedings%20or%20meet%20lawyers%2C%20among%20other%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said%20more%20and%20more%20women%20professionals%20are%20seen%20in%20important%20posts%20across%20the%20nation%20now.%20%26quot%3BEarlier%2C%20the%20law%20profession%20was%20an%20elite%20men%20profession%2C%20but%20now%20woman%20constitutes%2036%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20district%20judiciary.%20Over%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20recent%20selected%20candidates%20were%20also%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2041%20per%20cent%20of%20law%20clerks%20who%20assist%20judges%20are%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20last%20week%20designated%2011%20women%20lawyers%20as%20senior%20advocates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20near%20future%2C%20we%20must%20address%20the%20structural%20issues%20affecting%20the%20judiciary%2C%20such%20as%20pendency%20of%20cases%2C%20archaic%20procedures%2C%20and%20the%20culture%20of%20adjournments.%20Our%20effort%20in%20our%20work%20as%20judges%20and%20administrators%20must%20be%20to%20ensure%20dignity%20to%20the%20district%20judiciary%2C%20which%20is%20the%20first%20point%20of%20contact%20for%20citizens.%20Our%20ability%20to%20remain%20relevant%20as%20an%20institution%20requires%20us%20to%20recognise%20challenges%20and%20begin%20difficult%20conversations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%2C%20we%20must%20emerge%20out%20of%20the%20adjournment%20culture%20to%20a%20culture%20of%20professionalism%3B%20second%2C%20we%20have%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20length%20of%20oral%20arguments%20does%20not%20interminably%20delay%20judicial%20outcomes%3B%20third%2C%20the%20legal%20profession%20must%20provide%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20for%20first-generation%20lawyers%20-%20men%2C%20women%2C%20and%20others%20from%20marginalised%20segments%20who%20have%20the%20will%20to%20work%20and%20the%20potential%20to%20succeed%2C%20and%20fourth%2C%20let%20us%20begin%20the%20conversation%20on%20long%20vacations%20and%20whether%20alternatives%20such%20as%20flexitime%20for%20lawyers%20and%20judges%20is%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20