0need%20to%20stop%20condoning%20abuse%20in%20the%20name%20of%20artistry.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Insat-3DS%20satellite%20sent%20to%20spaceport%2C%20launch%20soon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706431499000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107202094%2Cimgsize-803795.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Finsat-3ds-satellite-sent-to-spaceport-launch-soon%2Farticleshow%2F107202034.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Isro%20concludes%20vital%20tests%20on%20the%20Insat-3DS%20satellite%20at%20the%20UR%20Rao%20Satellite%20Centre%2C%20marking%20progress%20in%20India's%20climate%20observatory%20initiative.%20The%20satellite%2C%20geared%20towards%20bolstering%20meteorological%20observations%20and%20disaster%20warning%20capabilities%2C%20is%20headed%20to%20Sriharikota%20for%20the%20GSLV-F14%20mission%2C%20slated%20between%20Feb%2017%20and%20March%2017%2C%20with%20a%20mid-Feb%20target.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TNN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Finsat-3ds-satellite-sent-to-spaceport-launch-soon%2Farticleshow%2F107202034.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20Exit%20Is%20Big%20Setback%20For%20INDIA%2C%20Facepalm%20For%20Congress%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20response%20to%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20the%20BJP%20government%20last%20year%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20said%20the%20Opposition's%20INDIA%20bloc%20was%20bowling%20one%20no-ball%20after%20the%20other.%20Five%20months%20later%2C%20political%20developments%20in%20Bihar%20have%20provided%20BJP%20nothing%20less%20than%20a%20full%20toss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJDU%20leader%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20move%20to%20end%20his%20alliance%20with%20the%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav-led%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20to%20revive%20his%20tie-up%20with%20the%20BJP%20comes%20as%20a%20massive%20setback%20to%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20months%20before%20it%20takes%20on%20the%20formidable%20BJP%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20What's%20more%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%2C%20in%20his%20first%20remarks%20after%20submitting%20his%20resignation%2C%20referred%20to%20how%20%26quot%3Bnobody%20was%20working%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20latest%20flip-flop%20hits%20INDIA%20bloc%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBengal%2C%20Punjab%20And%20Now%20Bihar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bihar%20reversal%20comes%20amid%20the%20friction%20within%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20to%20reach%20a%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%20with%20regional%20forces%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party.%20Trinamool%20supremo%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Congress%20amid%20seat-sharing%20talks%20and%20virtually%20pulled%20the%20plug%20on%20an%20INDIA%20alliance%20in%20the%20state.%20She%20has%20said%20Trinamool%20will%20contest%20alone%20and%20a%20decision%20on%20any%20alliance%20would%20be%20taken%20only%20after%20the%20election.%20The%20Congress%20has%20since%20been%20busy%20in%20damage%20control%20and%20has%20stressed%20that%20they%20are%20working%20to%20find%20a%20way%20out.%20Seat-sharing%20talks%20have%20also%20hit%20a%20roadblock%20in%20Punjab%2C%20where%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20has%20said%20the%20AAP%20is%20gearing%20up%20for%20a%20solo%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%2C%20the%20Bihar%20developments%20mean%20advantage%20for%20BJP%20is%20what%20was%20till%20yesterday%20an%20Opposition-ruled%20state.%20The%20fact%20that%20Bihar%20has%20as%20many%20as%2040%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20makes%20it%20very%20significant%20politically%2C%20and%20the%20bigger%20picture%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20factor%20that%20made%20the%20BJP%20received%20Mr%20Kumar%2C%20infamous%20for%20his%20flip-flops%2C%20back%20into%20the%20NDA%20fold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBig%20Dent%20On%20Congress%20Image%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20Mr%20Kumar's%20resignation%2C%20his%20close%20aide%20and%20senior%20JDU%20leader%20KC%20Tyagi%20launched%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20the%20Congress%2C%20accusing%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20of%20trying%20to%20hijack%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%20This%2C%20he%20said%2C%20had%20forced%20the%20JDU%20to%20quit%20the%20alliance%20even%20after%20Mr%20Kumar%20was%20at%20the%20forefront%20to%20bring%20Opposition%20forces%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tyagi%20said%20the%20kind%20of%20preparations%20required%20to%20take%20on%20the%20BJP's%20formidable%20election%20machinery%20were%20nowhere%20to%20be%20seen%20even%20months%20before%20the%20big%20election.%20He%20also%20alleged%20that%20while%20the%20Congress%20was%20not%20open%20to%20letting%20allies%20contest%20in%20its%20strongholds%2C%20it%20kept%20pushing%20for%20more%20seats%20in%20states%20dominated%20by%20other%20Opposition%20parties.%20%26quot%3BCongress%20is%20fighting%20for%20its%20survival.%20And%20it%20now%20wants%20to%20finish%20off%20regional%20forces%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tyagi%20said.%20He%20also%20targeted%20the%20Congress%20over%20the%20delay%20in%20finalising%20seat-sharing%20arrangements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JDU%20leader's%20remarks%20plays%20out%20against%20regional%20parties'%20repeated%20assertions%20that%20they%20should%20be%20given%20a%20bigger%20role%20in%20their%20bastions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJDU's%20exit%20from%20INDIA%20will%20further%20push%20Congress%20on%20the%20back%20foot%20as%20regional%20parties%20are%20likely%20to%20use%20the%20Bihar%20developments%20to%20drive%20a%20hard%20bargain%20in%20seat-sharing.%20%26quot%3BThe%20alliance%20has%20ended%20because%20of%20Congress's%20arrogance%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tyagi%20said%2C%20also%20predicting%20that%20other%20regional%20parties%20will%20also%20walk%20out%20of%20the%20alliance%20with%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20Mr%20Kumar's%20flip-flop%2C%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20has%20said%20there%20are%20many%20people%20like%20'Aaya%20Ram%2C%20Gaya%20Ram'%20in%20politics%20and%20that%20the%20party%20knew%20this%20would%20happen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP's%20Stability%20Narrative%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20was%20formed%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20pushing%20the%20narrative%20that%20a%20coalition%20of%20so%20many%20partners%20--%20who%20are%20also%20rivals%20in%20many%20states%20--%20is%20bound%20to%20be%20unstable.%20Last%20year%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20said%20the%20NDA%20had%20brought%20stability%20to%20the%20country.%20With%20Mr%20Kumar%2C%20among%20the%20key%20faces%20of%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20exiting%20the%20alliance%2C%20the%20BJP's%20claims%20regarding%20the%20inherent%20instability%20of%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20have%20got%20credence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20country%20gears%20up%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20next%20year%2C%20the%20BJP%20now%20appears%20a%20formidable%20force%20armed%20with%20the%20charisma%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20a%20meticulous%20election%20machinery.%20The%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20still%20struggling%20to%20put%20its%20house%20in%20order.%20And%20the%20recent%20exit%20of%20JDU%20will%20not%20help%20its%20public%20perception.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706431320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fm2qhajq8_opposition-meet_625x300_12_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-india-bloc-bihar-political-crisis-why-nitish-kumars-latest-flip-flop-is-a-full-toss-for-bjp-ahead-of-polls-4946753%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20his%20response%20to%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20the%20BJP%20government%20last%20year%2C%20Prime%20Minis