0minister%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20has%20assured%20the%20protesting%20workers%20he%20will%20look%20into%20their%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20strike%20was%20triggered%20by%20threats%20the%20workers%20allegedly%20faced%20when%20they%20asked%20their%20supervisors%20at%20Global%20Ventures%2C%20a%20contract%20firm%20that%20handles%20sanitation%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20to%20release%20their%20wages%20on%20time.%20Their%20salaries%20were%20eventually%20released%20on%20January%2019%2C%202024%2C%20much%20beyond%20the%20stipulated%20time%2C%20after%20they%20demonstrated.%20According%20to%20the%20Payment%20of%20Wages%20Act%2C%201936%2C%20the%20previous%20month%E2%80%99s%20salary%20should%20be%20paid%20up%20to%20the%207th%20or%2010th%20of%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20not%20the%20first%20time%20when%20the%20workers%20had%20to%20struggle%20to%20get%20their%20wages%20on%20time.%20Workers%20are%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20the%20supervisors%20of%20the%20company%20who%20act%20like%20overlords%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Harish%20Gautam%2C%20one%20of%20the%20trade%20union%20leaders%20at%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGautam%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20sanitation%20workers%20who%20are%20women%20have%20to%20constantly%20face%20abuses.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20asked%20for%20sexual%20favours%20very%20often%20and%20told%20by%20the%20company%20staff%20that%20if%20they%20do%20not%20heed%20to%20their%20demands%2C%20they%20will%20lose%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gautam%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20sanitation%20staff%20at%20the%20hospital%20have%20been%20hired%20by%20the%20contract%20firm%20and%20should%20get%20a%20minimum%20of%20a%20little%20over%20Rs%2017%2C000%20per%20month%20as%20salary.%20However%2C%20workers%20complained%20that%20their%20salaries%20were%20abruptly%20cut%20by%20the%20contract%20firm%20almost%20every%20month.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20the%20basic%20demand%20to%20release%20salaries%20on%20time%20is%20taken%20as%20an%20affront%20by%20the%20supervisors.%20As%20many%20of%20these%20workers%20are%20not%20very%20well%20educated%2C%20they%20are%20marked%20absent%2C%20or%20on%20sanctioned%20leave%2C%20by%20the%20company%20very%20frequently.%20These%20mostly%20work%20as%20threats%20to%20workers%20in%20reality%2C%20who%20feel%20that%20they%20are%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20the%20company%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Maya%20John%2C%20a%20Delhi%20University%20professor%20who%20has%20been%20helping%20the%20workers%20organise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGautam%20said%20that%20most%20months%2C%20workers%20are%20unsure%20about%20the%20amount%20that%20will%20be%20credited%20in%20their%20bank%20accounts.%20%E2%80%9COne%20can%20get%20any%20amount.%20It%20is%20sometimes%20Rs%208%2C000%2C%20sometimes%20Rs%2011%2C000%2C%20much%20lower%20than%20the%20prescribed%20minimum%20wage.%20Complaints%20by%20workers%20are%20used%20by%20the%20company%20on%20most%20occasions%20as%20a%20reason%20to%20fire%20them%20on%20some%20illegitimate%20ground%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Gautam%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20supervisors%20often%20tell%20the%20workers%20to%20not%20reveal%20that%20they%20have%20received%20an%20amount%20lower%20than%20the%20minimum%20wage%20of%20Rs%2017%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20at%20least%20two%20FIRs%20filed%20last%20year%20against%20the%20sanitation%20supervisors%20by%20women%20workers%20who%20alleged%20that%20they%20were%20either%20sexually%20assaulted%20or%20asked%20for%20sexual%20favours.%20However%2C%20John%20said%20that%20not%20much%20was%20done%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20to%20keep%20a%20check%20on%20the%20supervisors.%20%E2%80%9CUsually%2C%20the%20supervisors%20ask%20for%20sexual%20favours%20from%20women%20who%20are%20widowed%20or%20unmarried%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gautam%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F28131731%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-28-at-10.55.45-AM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22817%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F28131731%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-28-at-10.55.45-AM.jpeg%20817w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F28131731%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-28-at-10.55.45-AM-300x230.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694690%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22626%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFemale%20sanitation%20workers%20protesting.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECuriously%2C%20the%20hospital%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20mandatory%20Internal%20Complaints%20Committee%20that%20looks%20into%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20at%20the%20workplace.%20The%20FIRs%20and%20a%20letter%20by%20some%20women%E2%80%99s%20organisations%20to%20the%20medical%20director%20of%20the%20hospital%20forced%20the%20hospital%20management%20to%20hastily%20put%20together%20an%20ICC%20unit%20in%20December%202023.%20Yet%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20organisations%20said%20in%20the%20letter%20that%20the%20only%20ICC%20meeting%20last%20month%20that%20was%20held%20to%20inquire%20about%20some%20cases%20of%20alleged%20sexual%20harassment%20did%20not%20have%20any%20representation%20from%20the%20women%20sanitation%20workers.%20The%20ICC%20meeting%2C%20moreover%2C%20was%20convened%20not%20because%20of%20the%20complaints%20but%20on%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20medical%20director%20and%20Delhi%20government%E2%80%99s%20health%20secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20majority%20of%20these%20workers%20belong%20to%20the%20Dalit%20Valmiki%20community.%20Their%20living%20standards%20are%20low%20and%20they%20have%20historically%20been%20pushed%20down%20in%20the%20socio-economic%20ladder%20as%20%E2%80%98outcastes%E2%80%99%20meant%20to%20do%20only%20sanitation%20work.%20%E2%80%9COften%20these%20workers%20have%20to%20face%20casteist%20slurs%20by%20their%20employers%2C%E2%80%9D%20John%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGautam%20said%20that%20such%20exploitative%20practices%20are%20not%20unique%20to%20the%20Burari%20Hospital%2C%20as%20most%20hospitals%20of%20Delhi%20employ%20their%20sanitation%20workers%20through%20a%20contracting%20firm%2C%20which%20in%20this%20case%20is%20Global%20Ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20lack%20of%20job%20security%20as%20contract%20employees%20is%20the%20primary%20problem.%20Despite%20all%20protests%2C%20the%20workers%20remain%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20the%20firm%20and%20its%20supervisors.%20Usually%2C%20these%20firms%20run%20a%20nexus%20with%20hospital%20management%20to%20employ%20many%20corrupt%20practices%20and%20also%20deny%20workers%20their%20rights%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gautam%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilar%20strikes%2C%20Gautam%20said%2C%20happened%20thrice%20last%20year%20when%20workers%20had%20to%20protest%20to%20get%20their%20salaries.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20hospital%20administration%20has%20been%20witness%20to%20these%20strikes%20and%20exploitative%20practices%20happening%20under%20their%20supervision.%20Yet%2C%20it%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20taken%20any%20action%20against%20the%20contract%20firm.%20This%20may%20only%20mean%20that%20both%20the%20firm%20and%20hospital%20management%20work%20in%20tandem%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20workers%20also%20alleged%20that%20many%20of%20these%20contract%20firms%20take%20a%20bribe%20of%20anywhere%20between%20Rs%2030%2C000%20and%2040%2C000%20to%20employ%20them.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20is%20unaccounted%20accumulation%20of%20wealth%20by%20these%20firms.%20If%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20pay%20the%20amount%2C%20you%20will%20not%20get%20a%20job.%20The%20practice%20is%20prevalent%20across%20Delhi%20hospitals%20at%20the%20time%20of%20employing%20contract%20workers%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Gautam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20workers%E2%80%99%20demonstrations%20bot