0he%20knew%20it%20would%20happen%2C%20adding%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20many%20people%20in%20the%20country%20like%20'%3Cem%3EAaya%20Ram-Gaya%20Ram%3C%2Fem%3E'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarlier%20he%20and%20us%20were%20fighting%20together.%20When%20I%20talked%20to%20Lalu%20Ji%20and%20Tejashwi%2C%20they%20also%20said%20that%20Nitish%20is%20going.%20If%20he%20wanted%20to%20stay%2C%20he%20would%20have%20stayed%20but%20he%20wants%20to%20go.%20That's%20why%20we%20already%20knew%20this%2C%20but%20to%20keep%20the%20India%20Alliance%20intact%2C%20if%20we%20say%20something%20wrong%2C%20the%20wrong%20message%20will%20be%20sent.%20This%20information%20was%20already%20given%20to%20us%20by%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20Tejashwi%20Yadav.%20Today%20that%20came%20true.%20There%20are%20many%20people%20in%20the%20country%20like%20'%3Cem%3EAaya%20Ram-Gaya%20Ram%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20national%20president%20Nitish%20Kumar%20arrived%20at%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20in%20Patna%20and%20handed%20over%20his%20resignation%20to%20Governor%20Rajendra%20Arlekar%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20comes%20amid%20a%20deafening%20buzz%20that%20Nitish%20would%20rejoin%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%2C%20bringing%20an%20end%20to%20the%20'Mahagathbandhan'%20rule%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fast-changing%20political%20events%20in%20the%20state%20were%20triggered%20by%20a%20social%20media%20post%20from%20former%20CM%20and%20RJD%20chief%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20daughter%2C%20Rohini%20Acharya%2C%20in%20which%20she%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20JD(U)%20saying%20that%20while%20the%20'socialist%20party'%20styles%20itself%20as%20progressive%2C%20its%20ideology%20shifts%20with%20the%20changing%20wind%20patterns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20ongoing%20political%20drama%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20legislative%20party%20meeting%20is%20underway%20