20up%20the%20political%20circles%20months%20ahead%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20eight-time%20Chief%20Minister%20Mr%20Kumar%20has%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP%20again.%20This%20is%20his%20fifth%20flip-flop%20in%20a%20decade%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20a%20swift%20decline%20in%20his%20popularity%20and%20party's%20electoral%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20MLAs%20in%20Bihar%20have%20given%20letters%20of%20support%20to%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20according%20to%20sources.%20The%20party%20MLAs%20also%20held%20a%20meeting%20in%20Patna%20today%2C%20shortly%20before%20Mr%20Kumar%20met%20Governor%20Rajendra%20Arlekar%20and%20put%20in%20his%20papers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20question%2C%20however%2C%20is%20why%20the%20BJP%20is%20ready%20to%20take%20him%20back%20into%20the%20NDA%20fold%20after%20his%20repeated%20jumps%20across%20the%20political%20aisle.%20NDTV%20looks%20at%20some%20of%20the%20factors%20behind%20the%20BJP's%20decision%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Blow%20To%20INDIA%20Bloc%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20key%20faces%20of%20the%20Opposition's%20INDIA%20bloc%20and%20was%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20forging%20the%20united%20front%20to%20take%20on%20the%20formidable%20BJP%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20has%20said%20it%20was%20Mr%20Kumar%20who%20convened%20INDIA%20meetings%20and%20that%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20was%20expecting%20him%20to%20fight%20the%20BJP%20till%20the%20end.%20A%20flip-flop%20at%20this%20stage%20leaves%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20red-faced%20months%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%C2%A0It%20also%20gives%20credence%20to%20the%20BJP's%20contention%20that%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20is%20an%20unstable%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20a%20flip-flop%20also%20means%20an%20advantage%20in%20Bihar%2C%20which%20has%2040%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20and%20was%20being%20seen%20as%20an%20INDIA%20stronghold%20so%20far.%20The%20ties%20between%20Congress%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20Bengal%2C%20and%20Congress%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20in%20Punjab%20are%20already%20strained%20over%20seat-sharing%20talks.%20An%20end%20to%20the%20RJD-JDU%20alliance%20in%20Bihar%20at%20this%20stage%20would%20mean%20more%20trouble%20for%20INDIA.%20While%20a%20section%20of%20state%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20been%20against%20taking%20Mr%20Kumar%20back%2C%20the%20central%20leadership%20may%20have%20green-lighted%20the%20move%20after%20looking%20at%20the%20larger%20picture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20State%20Equation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20has%20managed%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post%20despite%20his%20repeated%20flip-flops.%20His%20popularity%20and%20his%20party's%20electoral%20performance%2C%20however%2C%20has%20seen%20a%20consistent%20decline.%20His%20image%20of%20Sushashan%20Babu%20-%20the%20development%20man%20-%20has%20now%20been%20replaced%20as%20that%20of%20'paltu%20kumar'%20-%20the%20one%20who%20keeps%20switching%20sides%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20115%20seats%20in%20the%202010%20Bihar%20polls%20to%2071%20in%202015%20to%20just%2043%20in%202020%2C%20JDU's%20strength%20in%20the%20Assembly%20has%20been%20on%20a%20slide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20meant%20that%20despite%20Mr%20Kumar%20being%20in%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20chair%2C%20his%20party%20is%20the%20third-largest%20force%20in%20the%20Assembly.%20Be%20it%20RJD%20or%20BJP%2C%20Mr%20Kumar's%20autonomy%20has%20declined%20because%20it%20is%20his%20ally%20who%20has%20the%20more%20numbers.%20So%20the%20BJP%20knows%20that%20even%20if%20lets%20Mr%20Kumar%20retain%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post%2C%20it%20holds%20greater%20control%20than%20JDU%20in%20the%20Bihar%20government's%20decisions.%20That%20way%2C%20it%20is%20a%20win-win%20situation%20for%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Perception%20Game%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar's%20flip-flops%20over%20the%20past%20decade%20has%20adversely%20impacted%20his%20public%20image.%20The%20BJP%20knows%20that%20it%20stands%20to%20lose%20little%20in%20the%20perception%20game%20because%2C%20unlike%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20or%20Maharashtra%2C%20it%20is%20not%20a%20section%20of%20ruling%20party%20MLAs%20making%20a%20switch.%20In%20those%20states%2C%20the%20BJP%20was%20accused%20of%20engineering%20mutinies%20to%20topple%20governments.%20Here%2C%20with%20Mr%20Kumar%20repeatedly%20changing%20allies%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20not%20be%20seen%20as%20the%20villain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leaders%2C%20predictably%2C%20have%20gone%20back%20to%20their%20%26quot%3Bjungle%20raj%26quot%3B%20rhetoric%20to%20explain%20why%20they%20are%20ok%20with%20teaming%20with%20Mr%20Kumar%20again.%20%26quot%3BJungle%20Raj%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20term%20used%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20refer%20to%20the%20corruption-%20and%20crime-tainted%20tenure%20of%20the%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav-led%20RJD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20the%20biggest%20party%20in%20Bihar.%20We%20are%20alert%20and%20are%20tracking%20the%20developments%20closely.%20We%20are%20seized%20of%20the%20shifting%20political%20sands%20in%20Bihar.%20We%20will%20not%20take%20a%20step%20back%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20discharging%20our%20responsibilities.%20We%20cannot%20leave%20Bihar%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20'Jungle%20Raj'%2C%26quot%3B%20BJP%20national%20spokesperson%20Ajay%20Alok%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706423040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-08%2Fodv4leq8_nitish-modi_625x300_08_August_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-bjp-may-take-nitish-kumar-back-year-after-doors-have-closed-jab-4946179%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nitish%20Kumar%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20key%20faces%20of%20the%20Opposition's%20INDIA%20bloc%20and%20was%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20forging%20the%20united%20front%20to%20take%20on%20the%20formidable%20BJP.%20A%20flip-flop%20at%20this%20stage%20will%20leave%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20red-faced%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-bjp-may-take-nitish-kumar-back-year-after-doors-have-closed-jab-4946179%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-bjp-may-take-nitish-kumar-back-year-after-doors-have-closed-jab-4946179%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-bjp-may-take-nitish-kumar-back-year-after-doors-have-closed-jab-4946179%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nitish%20Kumar%20Resigns%20as%20Bihar%20CM%2C%20to%20Form%20Government%20Again%20in%20Alliance%20With%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F28115337%2FGEw_SguXMAAOp8I.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENitish%20Kumar%20on%20Sunday%20(January%2028)%20morning%20met%20Bihar%20governor%20Governor%20Rajendra%20Arlekar%20and%20resigned%20as%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state.%20He%20is%20expected%20to%20stake%20claim%20to%20form%20the%20government%20again%2C%20but%20this%20time%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20rather%20than%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20governor%20has%20accepted%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20leader%E2%80%99s%20resignation%2C%20PTI%20reported%2C%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20continue%20as%20the%20caretaker%20chief%20minister%20until%20the%20new%20government%20is%20formed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20his%20resignation%2C%20Nitish%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20working%20on%20an%20alliance%20(INDIA)%20for%20the%20last%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years%20but%20things%20were%20not%20working%20out.%20Now%2C%20we%20will%20form%20a%20new%20alliance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twit