inister%20is%20famous%20for%20his%20regular%20shifts%20between%20alliances%2C%20irrespective%20of%20ideology.%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fayaram-gayaram-politics-of-nitish-at-play-poised-to-rejoin-nda%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Nitish%20has%20a%20habit%20of%20being%20fickle%20towards%20his%20allies.%20In%202017%2C%20the%20RJD%20was%20in%20the%20dark%20when%20Nitish%20suddenly%20announced%20his%20decision%20to%20quit%20the%20Mahagathbandhan.%20Then%2C%20when%20he%20left%20the%20BJP%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20leaders%20too%20had%20no%20clue%2C%20until%20he%20announced%20his%20decision%20to%20again%20switch%20camps.%20Reports%20now%20suggest%20that%20even%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%2C%20with%20whom%20Nitish%20goes%20back%20a%20long%20time%20both%20as%20friend%20and%20foe%2C%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20aware%20of%20any%20new%20move%20by%20Nitish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINDIA%20alliance%20leaders%20have%20criticised%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20move.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20Ram%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20Paltu%20Ram%20in%20Bihar.%20The%20BJP%20and%20Amit%20Shah%20himself%20had%20called%20Nitish%20Paltu%20Ram%20when%20he%20had%20joined%20hands%20with%20Lalu.%20Shah%20had%20said%20that%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20doors%20are%20closed%20for%20Nitish%20Kumar.%20Now%20what%20happened%20to%20that%3F%20The%20BJP%20people%20are%20the%20bigger%20Paltu%20Ram%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%E2%80%99s%20Sanjay%20Raut%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20people%20like%20this%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAaya%20Ram%2C%20Gaya%20Ram%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%B6%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E2%80%98%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AE-%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%