.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fun-to-punish-staffers-involved-in-terror-urges-unrwa-funding-guterres%2Famp_articleshow%2F107198990.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fun-to-punish-staffers-involved-in-terror-urges-unrwa-funding-guterres%2Famp_articleshow%2F107198990.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%20Stage%20Collapses%20At%20Singer%20B%20Praak's%20Event%20At%20Delhi%20Temple%2C%201%20Dead%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOne%20woman%20was%20killed%20and%2017%20people%20were%20injured%20after%20a%20stage%20for%20seating%20devotees%20at%20a%C2%A0jagran%20collapsed%20at%20Delhi's%20Kalkaji%20Temple%2C%20police%20said%20on%20Sunday.%20The%2045-year-old%20woman%20was%20rushed%20to%20the%20hospital%20by%20two%20people%20in%20an%20autorickshaw%20but%20she%20was%20later%20declared%20dead.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20the%20event%20was%20organised%20without%20permission%20on%20Friday%20night%20and%20was%20attended%20by%20over%201%2C600%20people.%C2%A0Videos%20of%20the%20jagran%2C%20an%20overnight%20devotional%20programme%2C%20showed%20a%20huge%20crowd%20of%20people%20inside%20the%20tightly-packed%20venue.%20Devotees%20had%20also%20climbed%20on%20the%20main%20stage%20where%20popular%20Punjabi%20musician%20B%20Praak%20was%20singing%20%3Cem%3Ebhajans%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20got%20a%20call%20at%20around%2012.30%20am%20that%20a%20stage%2C%20which%20was%20set%20up%20for%20'jagran'%20purpose%2C%20at%20Kalkaji%20temple%2C%20collapsed.%20Teams%20were%20rushed%20to%20the%20spot.%20One%20woman%20was%20declared%20dead.%20Further%20investigation%20is%20underway%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20police%20officer%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20the%20wooden%20platform%2C%20which%20was%20erected%20to%20seat%20the%20families%20of%20the%20event's%20organisers%20and%20other%20VIPs%2C%20had%20started%20leaning%20under%20excessive%20weight.%20At%20around%20midnig