er-causing%20chemicals%2C%20faces%20a%20government%20takeover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20closing%20down%20of%20Tata%20Steel%20has%20caused%20consternation%20among%202%2C800%20workers%20who%20could%20lose%20their%20jobs%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024.%20However%2C%20the%20firm%2C%20which%20employs%204%2C000%20workers%20totally%20at%20the%20furnaces%20in%20Port%20Talbot%2C%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20reassure%20the%20workers%20and%20unions%20that%20the%20decision%20is%20important%20for%20the%20long-term%20survival%20of%20the%20entire%20Port%20Talbot%20operation%2C%20but%20with%20little%20avail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fbusiness%2Findian-steelmakers-under-fire-tata-steel-stirs-anger-with-united-kingdom-green-turnaround-plan-arcelor-mittal-faces-government-take-over-in-italy-to-stay-afloat%2Fcid%2F1995061%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Tata%20Steel%20chief%20executive%20T.V.%20Narendran%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20ambitious%20plan%E2%80%9D%20is%20aimed%20at%20%E2%80%9Cguaranteeing%20long-term%2C%20high-quality%20steel%20production%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20transforming%20the%20Port%20Talbot%20facility%20into%20one%20of%20Europe%E2%80%99s%20premier%20centres%20for%20green%20steelmaking%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20changes%20include%20replacing%20coal-fired%20blast%20furnaces%20with%20less-polluting%2C%20lower-carbon%20electric%20arc%20furnaces%2C%20which%20the%20company%20says%2C%20will%20melt%20scrap%20steel%20rather%20than%20producing%20virgin%20steel%20from%20iron%20ore.%20According%20to%20the%20estimates%2C%20the%20change%20will%20ensure%20a%20reduction%20in%20the%20overall%20UK%20CO2%20emission%20by%201.5%25.%20However%2C%20the%20changes%20would%20take%20about%20three%20years%20and%20would%20come%20at%20the%20cost%20of%201.25%20billion%20pounds%20sterling%2C%20including%20500%20million%20pounds%20sterling%20paid%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20workers%2C%20union%20leaders%2C%20and%20politicians%20from%20the%20Labour%20Party%20do%20not%20buy%20into%20the%20version%20presented%20by%20the%20firm%20and%20the%20political%20establishment%20that%20is%20supporting%20the%20move.%20Calling%20it%20%E2%80%9Cindustrial%20vandalism%20on%20a%20grand%20scale%E2%80%9D%2C%20they%20demand%20the%20firm%20to%20keep%20at%20least%20one%20blast%20furnace%20open%20while%20the%20upgrade%20is%20ongoing.%20Unless%20their%20demands%20are%20not%20met%2C%20workers%20say%2C%20they%20would%20resort%20to%20industrial%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Mittal%E2%80%99s%20steel%20plant%20in%20Italy%E2%80%99s%20Taranto%20is%20ready%20to%20be%20taken%20over%20by%20the%20government%20amid%20environmental%20problems%20the%20firm%20has%20been%20facing%20and%20debts%20of%20%24200%20million%20it%20owes%20to%20its%20gas%20supplier.%20An%20Italian%20court%20has%20recently%20permitted%20the%20gas%20company%20to%20stop%20supply%20to%20the%20Mittal%20plant%2C%20which%20is%20among%20Europe%E2%80%99s%20largest%20steel%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvitalia%2C%20the%20Italian%20government%E2%80%99s%20state%20investment%20agency%2C%20which%20has%20a%20stake%20in%20the%20Taranto%20plant%2C%20has%20initiated%20legal%20proceedings%20to%20put%20in%20place%20a%20special%20administrator%20to%20oversee%20the%20process%20and%20planning%20to%20remove%20ArcelorMittal%20from%20the%20management.%20According%20to%20the%20newspaper%2C%20%E2%80%9Cspecial%20administration%E2%80%9D%20in%20Italy%20is%20a%20bankruptcy%20scheme%20intended%20to%20keep%20companies%20functioning%20while%20their%20financial%20problems%20are%20sorted%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20closure%20of%20the%20Mittal%20steel%20plant%20means%20the%20ousting%20of%20nearly%2010%2C000%20workers%20it%20employs%2C%20a%20fallout%20that%20Italian%20Prime%20Minister%20Giorgia%20Meloni%E2%80%99s%20government%20has%20been%20desperately%20trying%20to%20avoid.%20However%2C%20it%20wants%20ArcelorMittal%20to%20inject%20320%20million%20euros%20into%20the%20steelworks.%20In%20fact%2C%20economic%20development%20minister%20Adolfo%20Urso%20told%20the%20Italian%20parliament%20that%20%E2%80%9Cdrastic%20intervention%E2%80%9D%20is%20needed%20to%20save%20the%20steel%20plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20ArcelorMittal%20says%20it%20is%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20do%20so%20given%20the%20Taranto%20plant%20has%20been%20suffering%20from%20major%20environmental%20problems%20since%20Mittal%20took%20over%20the%20plant%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issues%20faced%20by%20both%20Tata%20Steel%20and%20ArcelorMittal%20bring%20to%20the%20fore%20the%20challenges%20being%20faced%20by%20steel%20producers%20in%20Europe%20and%20the%20UK%2C%20where%20firms%20face%20an%20uphill%20task%20to%20stay%20afloat%20given%20high%20environmental%20awareness%20and%20expensive%20unionised%20labours.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706413492000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F28090825%2FEffect-88.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fthousands-set-to-lose-jobs-as-tata-steel-in-the-uk-arcelormittal-in-italy-on-the-verge-of-shutdown%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nearly%2013%2C000%20workers%20in%20total%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20ousted%20from%20work%20as%20the%20two%20prominent%20Indian%20steel%20manufacturers%20in%20the%20region%20face%20a%20host%20of%20environmental%20and%20financial%20problems.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fthousands-set-to-lose-jobs-as-tata-steel-in-the-uk-arcelormittal-in-italy-on-the-verge-of-shutdown%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farmers%20vow%20Paris%20'siege'%20in%20pay%2C%20conditions%20battle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706412797000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107197476%2Cimgsize-1630793