ions%20move%20around.%20They%20had%20swords%20and%20rods%2C%20and%20then%20they%20pelted%20stones.%20They%20smashed%20a%20TV%20in%20my%20house%2C%20they%20burnt%20a%20nearby%20eatery.%20This%20is%20very%20dangerous.%20We%20expected%20a%20rally%20to%20celebrate%20the%20temple%2C%20but%20didn%E2%80%99t%20expect%20to%20be%20targeted%20this%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Belim.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20local%20whose%20name%20is%20being%20withheld%20over%20his%20safety%20concerns%20said%20he%20has%20videos%20of%20known%20and%20local%20faces%20in%20the%20rally%2C%20but%20he%20does%20not%20want%20to%20identify%20them%20to%20police%20as%20one%20of%20his%20sons%20is%20under%20arrest.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20son%20is%20the%20only%20Muslim%20in%20his%20college%2C%20he%20is%20a%20gold-medallist%20in%20sports.%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20goons%20had%20had%20their%20eye%20on%20him%20for%20long%2C%20and%20now%20he%20is%20under%20arrest%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20videos%20of%20locals%20wielding%20swords%20and%20pelting%20stones%20at%20our%20homes%2C%20but%20I%20am%20scared%20that%20if%20I%20report%20against%20Hindus%2C%20either%20I%20will%20myself%20be%20arrested%20or%20my%20family%20will%20face%20security%20issues.%20All%20of%20us%20know%20it%20was%20a%20planned%20attack%20and%20meant%20to%20provoke%20us.%E2%80%9D%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20neighbour%2C%20one%20Shaista%2C%20is%20also%20under%20similar%20stress.%20Her%20husband%2C%20Wazeer%20Mohammed%20Saadiq%20Ali%20was%20not%20only%20beaten%2C%20but%20had%20to%20get%20six%20stitches%20on%20the%20back%20of%20his%20head%20because%20of%20the%20violence.%20%E2%80%9CPolice%20broke%20into%20every%20home.%20They%20dragged%20my%20husband%20away%20and%20hit%20him%20severely.%20They%20even%20took%20all%20our%20phones%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20Their%20daughter%2C%20a%20