2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20weeks%20ago%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20had%20said%20that%20the%20difference%20in%20approach%20to%20the%20similar%20allegations%20made%20by%20Canada%20and%20the%20United%20States%20was%20because%20the%20latter%20had%20shared%20information.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20is%20when%20the%20Americans%20believed%20they%20had%20an%20issue%2C%20whether%20their%20belief%20is%20validated%20or%20not%20only%20the%20court%20can%20decide%2C%20they%20came%20to%20us%20and%20said%20look%20we%20have%20these%20concerns%20and%20we%20are%20sharing%20this%20with%20you%20and%20would%20like%20you%20to%20find%20out%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening.%20The%20Canadians%20did%20not%20do%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fcanada-not-us-uses-freedom-of-speech-to-justify-extremism-jaishankar%2Farticleshow%2F106708212.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20a%20reiteration%20of%20what%20he%20had%20said%20last%20month%20after%20India%20had%20set%20up%20a%20high-level%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20the%20accusation%20made%20by%20US%20investigators.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20November%2029%2C%20US%20federal%20prosecutors%20charged%20an%20Indian%20citizen%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20with%20collaborating%20with%20an%20Indian%20government%20official%20in%20a%20foiled%20plot%20to%20assassinate%20Khalistani%20separatist%20lawyer%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20who%20holds%20dual%20citizenship%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Canada.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnikhil-gupta-pannun-assassination-plot-documents%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Nick%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20Money%20Courier%20and%20a%20Hitman%3A%20What%20New%20Documents%20Say%20About%20The%20Pannun%20Murder%20Plot%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CInsofar%20as%20Canada%20is%20concerned%2C%20no%20specific%20evidence%20or%20inputs%20were%20provided%20to%20us.%20So%20the%20question%20of%20equitable%20treatment%20to%20two%20countries%2C%20one%20of%20whom%20has%20provided%20input%20and%20one%20of%20whom%20has%20not%2C%20does%20not%20arise%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fone-has-provided-inputs-another-hasnt-jaishankar-on-indias-differing-responses-to-us-canada%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EJaishankar%20had%20said%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20December%207%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20has%20been%20no%20reaction%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%20over%20the%20claims%20made%20by%20the%20senior%20outgoing%20official%20of%20the%20Trudeau%20administration%20on%20this%20ostensible%20change%20in%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20position.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndian%20NSA%E2%80%99s%20role%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThomas%20specifically%20noted%20that%20her%20discussions%20with%20her%20counterpart%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20national%20security%20advisor%20Ajit%20Doval%2C%20were%20positive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20RCMP%20investigation%20is%20well%20underway%20and%20so%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20speak%20too%20much%20about%20it.%20The%20RCMP%20will%20hopefully%20be%20able%20to%20prosecute%20the%20individuals%20accountable%20and%20responsible.%20But%20my%20discussions%20with%20my%20counterpart%20in%20India%20have%20been%20fruitful%20and%20I%20think%20they%E2%80%99ve%20moved%20things%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20stated.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20India%E2%80%99s%20position%20had%20changed%2C%20Thomas%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20very%20much%20an%20evolution%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20Trudeau%20made%20the%20explosive%20accusations%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20Canadian%20parliament%2C%20India%20had%20reacted%20angrily%2C%20describing%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9Cabsurd%E2%80%9D.%20Subsequently%2C%20both%20nations%20expelled%20a%20senior%20diplomat%20each.%20India%20took%20additional%20measures%20by%20suspending%20visa%20services%20for%20Canadian%20nationals%2C%20a%20restriction%20that%20was%20lifted%20after%20a%20month.%20Additionally%2C%20Canada%20was%20compelled%20to%20withdraw%20more%20than%2040%20diplomats%20as%20India%20insisted%20on%20parity%20on%20diplomatic%20presence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20government%20also%20insisted%20publicly%20that%20the%20main%20issue%20with%20Canada%20was%20that%20it%20was%20allowing%20Khalistani%20groups%20to%20thrive%20under%20the%20garb%20of%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20a%20question%20whether%20the%20improvement%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20relationship%20with%20Canada%20was%20due%20to%20the%20US%20indictment%2C%20Thomas%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20two%20are%20connected%20for%20sure%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnikhil-gupta-pannun-assassination-plot-documents%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20unsealed%20November%20indictment%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20alleged%20that%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20had%20told%20a%20hitman%20that%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20hire%20that%20there%20were%20several%20jobs%20in%20Canada%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20evening%20of%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20killing%20on%20June%2018%2C%20the%20unnamed%20Indian%20government%20official%20had%20shared%20a%20video%20of%20the%20Canadian%20citizen%20slumped%20at%20his%20vehicle%20to%20Gupta.%20He%20promptly%20forwarded%20it%20to%20a%20criminal%20associate%20helping%20him%20to%20recruit%20a%20hitman%2C%20later%20revealed%20to%20be%20an%20under