eeting.%20(A%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20the%20very%20blatant%20manner%20in%20which%20she%20has%20now%20gone%20public%20%E2%80%93%20a%20sure%20measure%20of%20the%20changing%20times!).%20To%20further%20ingratiate%20herself%20with%20the%20powers%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Nagpur%2C%20she%20also%20brought%20in%20the%20Bharat-India%20divide%2C%20by%20claiming%20that%20her%20group%20was%20from%20%E2%80%9Csmall%20town%20India%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20Lutyen%E2%80%99s%20Delhi%20types%20in%20the%20Academy%20did%20not%20share%20her%20sentiments.%20She%20had%20been%20issued%20a%20disciplinary%20notice%20by%20the%20Administration%20at%20that%20time%20but%20we%20are%20not%20aware%20of%20what%20happened%20to%20that.%20Presumably%2C%20nothing%2C%20since%20she%20has%20been%20elevated%20to%20the%20rarefied%20heights%20of%20the%20Apex%20scale%20and%20clearly%20entertains%20even%20loftier%20ambitions.%20Her%20post%20has%20attracted%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%20on%20social%20media%20and%20a%20flutter%20in%20the%20IAS%20fold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20335px)%2085vw%2C%20335px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F27173819%2F53536642_413894839368709_8464962425349734400_n.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22335%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F27173819%2F53536642_413894839368709_8464962425349734400_n.jpg%20513w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F27173819%2F53536642_413894839368709_8464962425349734400_n-300x296.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694624%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22330%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EManisha%20Patankar%20Mhaiskar.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20Mhaiskar%20did%2032%20years%20ago%20should%20be%20of%20no%20relevance%20now%2C%20especially%20as%20she%20was%20a%20young%20probationer%20then%2C%20still%20sowing%20her%20wild%20oats.%20What%20her%20personal%20religious%20or%20political%20affiliation%20is%20presently%20should%20also%20be%20of%20no%20concern%20to%20us%3A%20she%20is%20certainly%20entitled%20to%20them%20as%20a%20free%20citizen%20of%20a%20(still)%20free%20nation.%20It%20is%20when%20she%20goes%20public%20with%20them%2C%20in%20the%20most%20brazen%20and%20don%E2%80%99t-give-a-damn%20manner%2C%20that%20we%20should%20start%20worrying.%20The%20concern%2C%20therefore%2C%20should%20be%20that%20she%20has%20the%20confidence%20to%20publicly%20proclaim%20and%20reiterate%20those%20feelings%20in%202024%2C%20after%20having%20taken%20an%20oath%20to%20a%20(still)%20secular%20constitution%20and%20having%20ostensibly%20served%20it%20for%2032%20years.%20There%20are%20a%20number%20of%20points%20to%20be%20noted%20here%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20A%20serving%20public%20servant%20is%20celebrating%20and%20applauding%20something%20which%20has%20been%20declared%20to%20be%20a%20crime%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20I%20am%20not%20talking%20here%20about%20what%20she%20did%20in%201992%2C%20but%20the%20fact%20that%20in%20her%20post%20she%20maintains%20that%20she%20holds%20the%20firm%20belief%20that%20what%20happened%20on%20December%206%2C%201992%2C%20was%20%E2%80%9Csomething%20powerful%2C%20something%20auspicious%2C%20something%20positive%E2%80%9D.%20In%20fact%2C%20she%20goes%20on%20to%20describe%20it%20as%20%E2%80%9Cseminal%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20By%20drawing%20a%20contrast%20between%20%E2%80%9Csmall%20towns%E2%80%9D%20and%20Lutyen%E2%80%99s%20Delhi%20in%20a%20mocking%20manner%20she%20is%20again%20feeding%20into%20the%20right-wing%20narrative%20that%20the%20idea%20of%20secularism%20is%20an%20elitist%20concept%20nurtured%20in%20the%20metros%2C%20and%20that%20it%20is%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9Csmall%20towners%E2%80%9D%20like%20her%20who%20represent%20the%20true%20ethos%20of%20India.%20This%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20music%20the%20bhakts%20like%20to%20hear.%20(Incidentally%2C%20Mhaiskar%20is%20no%20small%20towner%20%E2%80%93%20she%20comes%20from%20Nagpur%2C%20which%20has%20a%20population%20of%203%20million%20and%20is%20the%20second%20capital%20of%20Maharashtra!).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20There%20is%2C%20in%20her%20post%2C%20an%20obvious%20ambiguity%20about%20her%20belief%20in%20pluralism%20and%20secularism.%20This%20does%20not%20sit%20well%20with%20the%20oath%20she%20took%20to%20uphold%20the%20constitution%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20That%20she%20can%20publicly%20go%20on%20record%20with%20her%20feelings%20and%20beliefs%20with%20such%20aplomb%20and%20impunity%20clearly%20indicates%20that%20she%20is%20confident%20no%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20her%2C%20unlike%20the%20notice%20issued%20to%20her%20in%201992.%20(She%20can%2C%20obversely%2C%20expect%20a%20lot%20of%20support%20on%20social%20media%2C%20a%20manifold%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20followers.%20A%20few%20approving%20phone%20calls%20from%20Delhi%2C%20and%20envious%20glances%20from%20her%20colleagues%20who%20would%20be%20kicking%20themselves%20for%20not%20having%20thought%20of%20a%20similar%20stratagem).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%C2%A0%20The%20timing%20of%20the%20post%20indicates%20that%20Mhaiskar%E2%80%99s%20repeat%20epiphany%20is%20not%20a%20spontaneous%20Wordsworthian%20%3Ci%3E%E2%80%9Cmy%20heart%20leaps%20up%20in%20delight%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Emoment%2C%20but%20more%20a%20Shakespearean%C2%A0%3Ci%3E%E2%80%9Ca%20tide%20in%20the%20affairs%20of%20men%20which%2C%20taken%20at%20the%20flood%2C%20leads%20on%20to%20fortune%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Emoment.%3Ci%3E%20%3C%2Fi%3EIt%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20well-thought-out%20move%3B%20one%20could%20be%20excused%20for%20thinking%20that%20she%20has%20observed%20the%20rising%20tide%20in%20the%20Saryu%20river%20and%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20plunge.%20The%20conduct%20rules%20can%20wait.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20well-timed%20confession%20is%20also%20a%20measure%20of%20the%20deterioration%20of%20our%20civil%20services.%20It%20is%20bad%20enough%20that%20more%20and%20more%20retired%20civil%20servants%20(not%20just%20the%20re-employed%20ones)%20and%20defence%20forces%20veterans%20are%20jumping%20on%20to%20the%20majoritarian%20bandwagon%2C%20but%20it%20is%20now%20abundantly%20clear%20that%20the%20rot%20has%20spread%20even%20to%20the%20serving%20officers%20%E2%80%93%20this%20is%20an%20ill%20wind%20that%20can%20blow%20no%20good.%20For%20it%20is%20the%20apolitical%2C%20religion-neutral%C2%A0and%20non-partisan%20civil%20services%20and%20the%20army%20(not%20the%20politicians)%20which%20have%20held%20this%20country%20together%20for%2075%20years%20through%20wars%2C%20riots%2C%20changes%20of%20government%20and%20insurrections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20capacity%20to%20continue%20to%20do%20so%20in%20the%20even%20more%20tumultuous%20times%20ahead%20will%20be%20seriously%20eroded%20and%20compromised%20if%20they%20begin%20to%20align%20themselves%20with%20particular%20religious%20beliefs%20and%20political%20ideologies%20in%20their%20public%20life.%20A%20democratic%20government%20functions%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20trust%20between%20the%20public%20servants%20and%20the%20public%2C%20on%20the%20belief%20that%20civil%20servants%20are%20impartial%20and%20apolitical%3B%20once%20large%20sections%20of%20the%20public%20lose%20this%20trust%2C%20the%20efficacy%20of%20governance%20itself%20gets%20compromised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20plus%20side%2C%20of%20course%2C%20Mhaiskar%20has%20suddenly%20improved%20her%20chances%20of%20becoming%20chief%20secretary%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20but%20she%20will%20have%20made%20a%20Faustian%20bargain%20to%20do%20so.%20I%2C%20for%20one%2C%20would%20not%20have%20much%20trust%20in%20the%20kind%20of%20administration%20she%20would%20be%20heading.%20My%20primary%20worry%2C%20however%2C%20is%20this%3A%20now%20that%20the%20sacred%20Lakshman%20Rekha%20has%20been%20crossed%2C%20will%20there%20now%20be%20a%20stampede%20by%20others%20to%20do%20the%20same%2C%20in%20the%20classic%20FOMO%20or%20lemming%20pattern%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Favayshukla.blogspot.com%2F2024%2F01%2Fa-new-low-for-ias.html%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0was%20originally%20published%20on%20the%20author%E2%80%99s%20blog%2C%20View%20from%20%5BGreater%5D%20Kailash.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20lightly%20for%20style.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706358924000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2Fbabri-masjid-demolition.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanisha-patankar-mhaiskars-post-on-babri-masjid-demolition-points-to-the-new-low-for-the-ias%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Maharashtra%20cadre%20officer%20in%20a%20post%20after%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%2C%20revealed%20how%2C%20as%20a%20probationer%20in%20Mussoorie%2C%20she%20celebrated%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20on%20December%206%2C%201992.%20Her%20post%20has%20attracted%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%20on%20social%20media%20and%20a%20flutter%20in%20the%20IAS%20fold.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanisha-patankar-mhaiskars-post-on-babri-masjid-demolition-points-to-the-new-low-for-the-ias%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20ICJ%20Has%20Reinforced%20an%20International%20Order%20Based%20on%20International%20Law%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F26223056%2FGEyARHkXcAA2hnF-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20provisional%20orders%20of%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20in%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20application%20against%20Israel%20have%20reinforced%20the%20centrality%20of%20international%20law%20to%20the%20global%20order.%20An%20increasingly%20brutal%20invasion%20of%20Palestine%20by%20Israel%2C%20supported%20by%20the%20Global%20North%2C%20had%20created%20a%20sense%20of%20despondency%20about%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20international%20organisations%20and%20the%20possibility%20of%20justice%20for%20some%20of%20the%20most%20disadvantaged%20people%20in%20the%20world.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20the%20United%20States%2C%20in%20its%20invasions%20of%20Iraq%20and%20Afghanistan%2C%20had%20to%20pay%20lip%20service%20to%20the%20need%20for%20avoiding%20civilian%20casualties.%20If%20international%20law%20was%20not%20observed%20by%20the%20United%20States%20and%20its%20allies%2C%20it%20was%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20not%20publicly%20derided.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIsrael%2C%20undoubtedly%20having%20faced%20a%20tragic%20loss%20on%20October%207%2C%20chose%20to%20take%20a%20path%20that%20sought%20to%20deny%20international%20law.%20Open%20calls%20were%20made%2C%20as%20was%20noted%20by%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20in%20its%20opinion%2C%20by%20high-ranking%20officials%20including%20the%20President%20of%20Israel%2C%20blaming%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20for%20the%20October%207%20attacks.%20The%20logic%20for%20such%20an%20accusation%20was%20that%20if%20they%20were%20not%20complicit%20they%20would%20rise%20up%20against%20Hamas.%20How%20an%20oppressed%20and%20disempowered%20population%20living%20in%20constant%20fear%20of%20violence%20from%20Israel%20was%20supposed%20to%20rise%20up%20against%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20enemies%20is%20a%20question%20best%20left%20to%20be%20answered%20by%20Israeli%20polemicists.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fby-invoking-genocide-convention-icj-makes-it-clear-israels-killing-of-palestinians-is-not-war-but-crime%5C%22%3EBy%20Invoking%20Genocide%20Convention%2C%20ICJ%20Makes%20It%20Clear%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20Killing%20of%20Palestinians%20is%20Not%20%E2%80%98War%E2%80%99%20But%20Crime%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Regardless%2C%20the%20one%20basic%20principle%20of%20law%20that%20has%20been%20valued%20and%20observed%20across%20cultures%20and%20systems%20is%20that%20individuals%20are%20punished%20for%20crimes%20that%20they%20have%20committed.%20Their%20families%2C%20communities%20and%20nations%20have%20never%20been%20held%20responsible%20by%20association.%20America%2C%20after%20all%2C%20has%20been%20able%20to%20repair%20relations%20with%20Vietnam%2C%20Japan%20with%20South%20Korea%20and%20Chine%2C%20even%20Germany%20with%20Israel.%20The%20fact%20that%20the%20Americans%20committed%20war%20crimes%20in%20Vietnam%2C%20the%20Japanese%20butchered%20and%20oppressed%20the%20Chinese%20and%20Koreans%20and%20the%20Germans%20committed%20the%20holocaust%20does%20not%2C%20and%20cannot%2C%20mean%20that%20the%20citizens%20of%20these%20countries%20are%20to%20be%20punished%20for%20the%20crimes%20committed%20by%20their%20governments%20and%20fellow%20citizens.%20The%20unreasonable%20demand%20made%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20for%20their%20continued%20safety%2C%20essentially%20for%20them%20to%20hold%20on%20their%20lives%2C%20is%2C%20to%20put%20it%20mildly%2C%20horrifying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ICJ%20has%2C%20while%20declining%20to%20order%20a%20ceasefire%2C%20passed%20the%20following%20measures%2C%20with%20Justice%20Dalveer%20Bhandari%20of%20India%2C%20joining%20in%20the%20majority%20judgment%20ordering%20provisional%20measures.%20The%20Court%20has%20ordered%20Israel%20to%20ensure%20that%20acts%20of%20genocide%20do%20not%20take%20place%20in%20the%20Gaza%20strip.%20It%20has%20also%20ordered%20that%20Israel%20must%20punish%20incitement%20to%20genocide.%20Further%20orders%20include%20directions%20to%20Israel%20to%20allow%20humanitarian%20aid%20into%20Gaza%20and%20to%20protect%20Palestinians.%20Measures%20to%20safeguard%20evidence%20of%20such%20crimes%20have%20also%20been%20ordered.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FEyKPAUPJivc%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Have%20the%20ICJ%20Provisional%20Orders%20Pleased%20%20South%20Africa%20and%20Embarrassed%20Israel%3F%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20these%20measures%2C%20ordered%20by%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%2C%20should%20act%20as%20a%20moral%20deterrent%20to%20Israel.%20Enforcement%20of%20judgments%20of%20the%20Court%20have%20to%20be%20done%20by%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%2C%20where%20the%20US%20will%20likely%20block%20any%20action%20against%20Israel.%20As%20such%2C%20while%20the%20International%20Court%20may%20have%20passed%20a%20judgment%2C%20it%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20effectively%20enforced%20against%20Israel%20in%20the%20even%20that%20Israel%20chooses%20to%20ignore%20the%20Court%E2%80%99s%20order.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20real%20value%20of%20the%20Court%E2%80%99s%20order%2C%20however%2C%20lies%20not%20in%20any%20corporal%20enforcement%20of%20its%20judgments%20but%20as%20an%20important%20voice%20in%20the%20unbelievable%20tragedy%20that%20is%20unfolding%20in%20Palestine.%20At%20a%20time%20when%20the%20US%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Germany%20and%20Canada%20have%20sought%20to%20either%20turn%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20the%20Israeli%20government%E2%80%99s%20actions%20or%20actively%20participate%20in%20the%20ongoing%20genocide.%20Recognising%20the%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20as%20a%20protected%20class%20of%20persons%20will%20give%20the%20Israeli%20government%20some%20pause%20in%20its%20ongoing%20campaign.%20It%20will%20also%20surely%20bolster%20the%20large%20numbers%20of%20Israelis%20who%20want%20this%20war%20and%20the%20slaughter%20of%20the%20Palestinians%20to%20end.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20will%20also%20support%20the%20voices%20of%20the%20moderates%20in%20Palestine%2C%20and%20across%20the%20world%2C%20for%20that%20matter%2C%20who%20recognise%20that%20the%20only%20lasting%20solution%20is%20co-existence%20on%20equal%20terms.%20This%20is%20a%20small%20step%20towards%20sanity%2C%20but%20a%20badly%20needed%20one.%20It%20is%20also%20an%20opportunity%20for%20Israel%20to%20end%20this%20genocidal%20campaign%20which%20seems%20designed%20not%20to%20protect%20the%20Israels%20who%20were%20taken%20hostage%20but%20to%20further%20the%20days%20of%20the%20government%20of%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu.%20This%20is%20an%20opportunity%20which%20everyone%20must%20make%20the%20most%20of.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ESarim%20Naved%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20lawyer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706357519000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F26223056%2FGEyARHkXcAA2hnF-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhas-the-icj-reinforced-a-rules-based-international-order%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20is%20a%20small%20step%20towards%20sanity%2C%20but%20a%20badly%20needed%20one.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhas-the-icj-reinforced-a-rules-based-international-order%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Mood%20for%20Murder%20%7C%20Episode%2010%3A%20Saunf%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F27181756%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-27-at-6.13.40-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20the%20series%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffiction%2Fa-mood-for-murder-episode-1-tea%5C%22%3EEpisode%201%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffiction%2Fa-mood-for-murder-episode-2-roti%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEpisode%202%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffiction%2Fa-mood-for-murder-episode-3-paaya%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEpisode%203%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffiction%2Fa-mood-for-murder-episode-4-meat-mutton-parleg%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEpisode%204%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffiction%2Fa-mood-for-murder-episode-5%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEpisode%205%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffiction%2Fa-mood-for-murder-episode-6-tetrapak-lassi%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEpisode%206%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffiction%2Fa-mood-for-murder-episode-7-chashni%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEpisode%207%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffiction%2Fa-mood-for-murder-episode-8-with-spice%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEpisode%208%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffiction%2Fa-mood-for-murder-episode-9-coffee%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEpisode%209%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20Jamal%20who%20finally%20called%20Laadley%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20arrange%20a%20meeting.%20%E2%80%9CPolice%20have%20closed%20the%20case%2C%20but%20our%20Habib%20thinks%20that%20Rahman%20miyan%20was%20murdered.%20He%20wants%20to%20assemble%20everyone%20involved%20and%20discuss%20the%20matter.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EZaroor%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20by%20all%20means%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20have%20a%20meeting%2C%20Jamal%20bhai.%20I%20have%20no%20control%20over%20Kanwal%20and%20Nirmal.%20They%20won%E2%80%99t%20come%2C%20and%20neither%20do%20I%20want%20them%20here%2C%20but%20I%20will%20assemble%20all%20the%20others%3A%20Maulvi%20saheb%20and%20the%20boys%2C%20Abrar%20and%20Arshad%2C%20Salman%20bechara%20is%20in%20jail%2C%20but%20we%20can%20call%20his%20mother%20and%20Zaitoon%20nani.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBetter%20not.%20His%20mother%20will%20start%20wailing%20saying%20he%20is%20still%20in%20jail.%20Then%20Naseeban%20will%20also%20turn%20up%2C%20and%20they%E2%80%99ll%20have%20a%20big%20fight.%20We%20want%20a%20serious%20meeting.%20I%20will%20ask%20Achche%20chacha%20and%20Tara%20ma%E2%80%99am%20to%20be%20present%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShall%20I%20ask%20Abrar%20to%20make%20some%20paaya%3F%20He%20is%20free%20now.%20There%20will%20be%20rotis%20from%20my%20tandoor.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20Laadley!%20Habib%20is%20calling%20the%20meeting%20to%20solve%20the%20murder.%20We%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20eating%20paaya%20when%20the%20murderer%20is%20called%20out.%20Kamaal%20hai!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20had%20assembled%20at%20Laadley%E2%80%99s%20shop.%20The%20man%20in%20the%20sleeveless%20brown%20sweater%20and%20checked%20lungi%20was%20squatting%20upon%20the%20clay%20oven.%20Laadley%20had%20had%20it%20lit%20and%20had%20told%20him%20to%20have%20some%20kababs%20and%20rotis%20ready.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20serve%20it%20only%20if%20the%20murderer%20turns%20out%20to%20be%20Kanwal-Nirmal%2C%20or%20that%20Rana%2C%20or%20Salman%20%E2%80%93%20because%20he%20is%20already%20in%20jail.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20serve%20if%20it%20is%20one%20of%20the%20people%20present%20at%20the%20meeting.%20It%20will%20be%20very%20embarrassing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%20had%20also%20had%20plastic%20chairs%20arranged%20in%20rows%20facing%20the%20clay%20oven%2C%20which%20Jamal%20and%20Habib%20later%20rearranged%20into%20a%20large%20circle.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20always%20a%20circle%2C%20Laadley%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jamal%20had%20said%20sardonically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaulvi%20saheb%20and%20the%20senior%20boys%20were%20present%3B%20Abrar%20and%20Arshad%20were%20present%20too.%20Laadley%20had%20also%20invited%20Salman%E2%80%99s%20mother%20and%20Zaitoon%20nani%2C%20despite%20Jamal%E2%80%99s%20reluctance%2C%20out%20of%20a%20sense%20of%20fairness.%20Achche%20Lal%20had%20suggested%20that%20Mrs%20Pushpa%20Kumari%20come%20too%2C%20and%20bring%20with%20her%20Jamal%E2%80%99s%20parents.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20seems%20the%20children%20have%20solved%20the%20mystery%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiled.%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20and%20look%20at%20you%20%E2%80%93%20you%20were%20interrogating%20them%20only!%E2%80%9D%20said%20she.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20Constable%20Rana%20came%20to%20the%20meeting%2C%20with%20Shambhu%20riding%20pillion.%20He%20parked%20his%20motorcycle%20alongside%20the%20gutter%20and%20sat%20sidesaddle%20on%20it%2C%20such%20that%20he%20had%20full%20view%20of%20the%20proceedings.%20Shambhu%20stood%20by%2C%20not%20sure%20whether%20to%20go%20inside%20or%20be%20close%20to%20Rana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20Rana%3F%20You%E2%80%99ve%20also%20come%3F%E2%80%9D%20called%20out%20Achche%20Lal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20come%20to%20eat%20the%20Bhandara%2C%20sir.%20Then%20I%20heard%20about%20this%20meeting%2C%20so%20I%20thought%20I%20will%20also%20come%20and%20get%20enlightened%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Constable%20Rana.%20%E2%80%9CI%20brought%20Shambhu%20also.%20Aye%20Laadley%2C%20give%20me%20some%20saunf.%20I%20have%20eaten%20too%20much%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20burped%20at%20Shambhu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPolice%20has%20closed%20the%20murder%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20began%20ASI%20Achche%20Lal.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20now%20got%20the%20post%20mortem%20report%2C%20which%20indicates%20that%20Rahman%20miyan%20died%20due%20to%20some%20infection.%20He%20slipped%20into%20a%20coma%20around%20midnight%20and%20passed%20away%20in%20the%20morning.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSaheb%2C%20let%20Salman%20go%E2%80%A6%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20mother%20wailed%20from%20a%20chair%20and%20Jamal%20clucked%20impatiently.%20Zaitoon%20nani%20embraced%20her%20tightly%20and%20mumbled%20some%20platitude%20into%20her%20ear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20there%20was%20so%20much%20blood%3F%20We%20were%20told%20he%20was%20hit%20with%20the%20steam%20iron%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Laadley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20unconscious%20and%20fell%20on%20the%20steam%20iron.%20Then%20he%20hit%20his%20head%20against%20the%20counter%20top%20and%20everything%20crashed%20to%20the%20ground.%20There%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20bleeding%2C%20but%20it%20was%20not%20serious.%20The%20doctor%20said%20that%20there%20was%20no%20skull%20fracture%20or%20anything.%20It%20would%20have%20required%20a%20few%20stitches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20extra%20bleeding%20because%20Rahman%20miyan%20used%20to%20take%20blood%20thinners%20for%20his%20heart%2C%E2%80%9D%20Habib%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20the%20doctor%20had%20indicated%20even%20on%20that%20day%20that%20it%20might%20not%20have%20been%20an%20assault.%20So%20what%20happened%20then%3F%20Rahman%20miyan%20had%20a%20bad%20infection%20and%20he%20slipped%20into%20a%20coma%3F%20Why%20was%20he%20not%20taken%20to%20the%20hospital%3F%20Abrar%2C%20Arshad%2C%20why%20did%20you%20not%20call%20the%20doctor%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Jamal%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20Asghar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20okay%20when%20we%20left!%20He%20was%20coughing%20and%20wheezing%20but%20he%20was%20fine.%20He%20was%20already%20annoyed%20with%20us%20because%20I%20had%20brought%20Salman%20in%20when%20he%20was%20doing%20his%20accounts.%20He%20had%20had%20to%20put%20everything%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20Arshad%20lowered%20his%20voice%20and%20said%20apologetically%3A%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20then%20Rana%20sir%20had%20come.%20Rahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20accounts%20had%20remained%20incomplete%20all%20evening%20and%20he%20wanted%20to%20be%20alone%20and%20finish%20them.%20We%20left%20on%20his%20orders%2C%20and%20when%20we%20came%20back%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20he%20was%20no%20more.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20you%20left%20only%20after%20finishing%20all%20your%20work%3F%20You%20even%20washed%20Shambhu%E2%80%99s%20pateela%20in%20which%20you%20had%20brought%20chashni%20that%20evening%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Habib%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COh%20that%20was%20much%20earlier.%20That%20was%20when%20Jamal%20bhai%20and%20you%20had%20come%20and%20had%20wanted%20gulab%20jamun.%20Must%20have%20been%20around%207.30%2C%20Shambhu%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%207.30.%20I%20was%20closing%20my%20shop%20and%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20need%20the%20pateela%20that%20evening%2C%20so%20when%20you%20said%20that%20Jamal%20ji%20is%20asking%20for%20more%20chashni%20I%20gave%20my%20pateela%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shambhu%20confirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20were%20you%20eating%20so%20much%20gulab%20jamun%3F%20A%20pateela%20of%20chashni%3F%E2%80%9D%20exclaimed%20Jamal%E2%80%99s%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWell%2C%20the%20chashni%20is%20of%20some%20significance%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Tara.%20%E2%80%9CRahman%20miyan%20actually%20died%20of%20a%20serious%20diabetic%20complication.%20It%20is%20called%20diabetic%20ketoacidosis%20and%20it%20is%20triggered%20when%20a%20diabetic%20person%20has%20some%20infection%20and%20at%20the%20same%20time%20his%20blood%20sugar%20levels%20go%20unchecked.%20It%20produces%20high%20levels%20of%20blood%20acids%2C%20which%20poison%20the%20body.%20Now%20Rahman%20miyan%20did%20have%20a%20serious%20chest%20infection.%20I%20suppose%20we%20can%20blame%20the%20air%20for%20that.%20But%20also%20he%20was%20being%20apparently%20less%20careful%20about%20his%20food%20and%20medicines%20in%20his%20wife%E2%80%99s%20absence.%20All%20of%20these%20would%20have%20been%20contributing%20factors%20to%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20complication%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tara%20paused%20dramatically%20before%20she%20continued.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20if%20Rahman%20miyan%20was%20deliberately%20administered%20chashni%2C%20during%20a%20severe%20infection%2C%20that%20would%20definitely%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20complication.%20So%20Jamal%2C%20answer%20your%20mother%2C%20a%20pateela%20of%20chashni%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstable%20Rana%20leaned%20in%20with%20interest.%20Jamal%20and%20his%20mother%20both%20turned%20red.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20are%20you%20saying%2C%20ma%E2%80%99am%3F%20Please%20don%E2%80%99t%20make%20such%20jokes.%20He%20has%20already%20been%20treated%20as%20a%20suspect.%20I%20only%20meant%20that%20he%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20having%20so%20much%20chashni%20because%20he%20himself%20has%20sugar%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aamna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETara%20raised%20her%20hands%20in%20apology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20%3Cem%3Edidn%E2%80%99t%20%3C%2Fem%3Eask%20for%20more%20gulab%20jamuns%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jamal.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20does%20Shambhu%20keep%20lying%20and%20saying%20that%20I%20sent%20for%20more%20gulab%20jamuns%20and%20chashni%3F%20I%20only%20had%20one.%20Habib%20you%20were%20there!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20we%20only%20had%20one%20gulab%20jamun%20each%20and%20then%20we%20left%20together.%20I%20remember%20because%20it%20was%20my%20treat.%20Jamal%20bhai%20would%20not%20have%20ordered%20more%20since%20I%20was%20going%20to%20pay.%20So%20why%20does%20Shambhu%20keep%20saying%20he%20sent%20more%20chashni%20for%20Jamal%20bhai%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEveryone%20looked%20towards%20Shambhu%2C%20who%20merely%20shrugged%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHow%20would%20I%20know%20if%20Jamal%20ji%20had%20actually%20asked%20for%20one%20plate%20or%20several%20plates%3F%20That%20is%20what%20Arshad%20said%20to%20me%20%E2%80%93%20he%20asked%20for%20the%20whole%20pateela%20of%20chashni.%20But%20I%20have%20been%20telling%20the%20police%20this%20story%20for%20some%20time%20now%20and%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20Jamal%20ji%20has%20actually%20denied%20having%20asked%20for%20more%20chashni.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20just%20confused%20by%20what%20you%20were%20saying%2C%E2%80%9D%20shouted%20Jamal%20in%20agitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJamal%20bhai%20certainly%20did%20not%20ask%20for%20more%20gulab%20jamun.%20I%20can%20vouch%20for%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Habib.%20%E2%80%9CPerhaps%20Shambhu%20never%20sent%20more%20chashni%20nor%20his%20pateela%20over%20to%20Rahman%20miyan%2C%20but%20made%20up%20this%20whole%20story%20as%20a%20cover%20when%20he%20stole%20the%20tiffin%20carrier%2C%20to%20show%20that%20he%20had%20brought%20it%20back%20by%20mistake%2C%20together%20with%20his%20own%20pateela%3F%E2%80%9D%20Habib%20was%20thinking%20on%20his%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20make%20sense%2C%20Habib.%20That%20would%20mean%20there%20was%20no%20chashni%20to%20begin%20with%2C%20and%20the%20whole%20story%20was%20false.%20Whereas%20we%20are%20acting%20on%20the%20premise%20that%20somebody%20deliberately%20gave%20him%20chashni%20and%20brought%20on%20the%20coma%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tara%20intervened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArshad!%20You%20went%20and%20told%20Shambhu%20that%20I%20had%20wanted%20more%20gulab%20jamuns%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jamal%20suddenly%20realised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20Abrar%20and%20Arshad%20are%20the%20only%20two%20people%20who%20could%20very%20easily%20have%20administered%20it%20to%20Rahman%20miyan.%20Put%20it%20in%20the%20qorma%2C%20or%20put%20it%20in%20any%20other%20food%20item%3F%20They%20also%20knew%20about%20his%20diabetes%20and%20how%20careful%20he%20was%20generally%2C%E2%80%9D%20Habib%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20guessed%20it%20the%20moment%20we%20heard%20Shambhu%20say%20that%20he%20had%20sent%20a%20pateela%20full%20of%20chashni.%20But%20I%20think%20Habibi%20momentarily%20forgot%20our%20theory%2C%20when%20he%20decided%20to%20explore%20this%20fresh%20line%20of%20enquiry%20about%20Shambhu%20having%20made%20it%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Tara%20matter%20of%20factly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstable%20Rana%20had%20now%20descended%20from%20his%20motorcycle%20seat%20and%20come%20inside%20the%20shop%2C%20Shambhu%20trailing%20behind%20him.%20Rana%20was%20looking%20at%20ASI%20Achche%20Lal%20for%20his%20cue.%20But%20Achche%20Lal%20seemed%20lost%20in%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20night%20we%20saw%20Rahman%20miyan%20repeatedly%20insult%20Arshad%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jamal%20next%20offered%20a%20motive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20he%20continued%20to%20snap%20at%20both%20of%20them%20even%20when%20I%20was%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20Constable%20Rana%20said.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20treating%20them%20with%20disdain.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArshad%20and%20Abrar%20both%20seemed%20bemused.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20saying%20that%20we%20killed%20Rahman%20miyan%20because%20he%20was%20insulting%20us%3F%20Jamal%20bhai%2C%20everyone%20insults%20us%20all%20the%20time.%20Even%20Rana%20Sir%20insults%20us.%20We%20are%20used%20to%20it.%20If%20we%20go%20killing%20everyone%20for%20an%20insult%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20Arshad%20scoffed%20and%20Abrar%20hurriedly%20put%20a%20hand%20on%20his%20shoulder.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20was%20Rahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20style.%20He%E2%80%99d%20get%20irritated%20very%20quickly%2C%20like%20Jamal%20bhai%20only.%20But%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20really%20mind%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%20The%20maulvi%20nodded%20absentmindedly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20he%20also%20informed%20on%20people%2C%20on%20your%20friends%2C%20and%20everyone%20was%20peeved%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tara%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20nothing%20to%20inform%20on%20us.%20We%20knew%20everything%20that%20was%20told.%20We%20were%20usually%20there%20with%20him%20all%20the%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abrar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETara%20glanced%20at%20Jamal%20and%20Habib%2C%20as%20they%20seemed%20to%20run%20out%20of%20ideas%20regarding%20motive.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20head%20I%20was%20certain%20we%20had%20solved%20it.%20But%20there%20are%20so%20many%20details%20we%20had%20missed%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnly%20motive%20I%20suppose%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jamal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWell%20there%20was%20one%20other%20significant%20thing%20that%20happened%3A%20Rahman%20miyan%20announced%20that%20he%20was%20leaving%20the%20restaurant%20to%20his%20wife%E2%80%99s%20nephew%2C%E2%80%9D%20Habib%20remembered.%20%E2%80%9CArshad%20said%20that%20he%20could%20have%20managed%20it%20too.%20And%20Rahman%20miyan%20made%20fun%20of%20him%20for%20even%20thinking%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWho%20else%20would%20he%20give%20his%20restaurant%20to%20if%20not%20to%20his%20relative%3F%20He%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20children%20of%20his%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20Laadley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20suggesting%20that%20Abrar%20and%20Arshad%20had%20hoped%20to%20get%20the%20restaurant%20after%20Rahman%20miyan%2C%20and%20when%20they%20found%20out%20that%20he%20was%20going%20to%20give%20it%20to%20his%20wife%E2%80%99s%20nephew%20they%20killed%20him%20out%20of%20spite.%20That%20kind%20of%20motive%20exists%20in%20novels%20and%20in%20cinemas%3B%20in%20real%20life%20the%20servants%20know%20it%20will%20never%20come%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Zaitoon%20nani%20said%20with%20a%20smile.%20The%20boys%20from%20the%20madarsa%20smiled%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%20scowled%20at%20the%20man%20in%20the%20checked%20lungi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20always%20knew%20it%20was%20going%20to%20the%20nephew.%20She%20had%20been%20after%20his%20life%3B%20it%20was%20discussed%2C%20day%20and%20night%2C%20for%20the%20last%20one%20year.%20We%20never%20imagined%20it%20would%20come%20to%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20Arshad%20spoke%20with%20genuine%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMay%20I%20say%20something%3F%20Even%20I%20know%20what%20might%20have%20happened%2C%E2%80%9D%20Zaitoon%20nani%20said.%20She%20glowered%20at%20Abrar%20and%20Arshad%3A%20%E2%80%9CWere%20you%20just%20having%20fun%20at%20the%20poor%20man%E2%80%99s%20expense%3F%20You%20were%20irritated%20so%20gave%20him%20some%20chashni%20to%20aggravate%20his%20sickness%3F%E2%80%9D%20They%20remained%20quiet.%20Zaitoon%20nani%20turned%20to%20her%20audience%2C%20%E2%80%9CCooks%20do%20that.%20When%20I%20felt%20cheated%20by%20begum%20saheba%2C%20I%20would%20forget%20to%20put%20salt%2C%20or%20put%20too%20much%20masala%2C%20or%20leave%20the%20rice%2C%20or%20the%20gosht%20uncooked.%20What%20else%20could%20I%20do%3F%20These%20days%2C%20if%20there%20is%20a%20problem%2C%20people%20just%20leave%20work%20%E2%80%93%20look%20at%20Salman.%20He%20can%E2%80%99t%20hold%20a%20job%20%E2%80%93%20gets%20bored%2C%20or%20gets%20upset%20and%20stops%20working.%20We%20did%20not%20have%20that%20option.%20Anyway%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20they%20would%20dare%20to%20murder%20somebody%20like%20Rahman%20miyan.%20What%20exactly%20did%20you%20do%20boys%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20raised%20her%20chin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAbrar%20bhai%20used%20to%20put%20whatever%20ingredients%20he%20liked%20into%20the%20paaya%20and%20if%20I%20told%20him%20that%20Rahman%20miyan%20would%20not%20like%20it%2C%20he%20would%20say%20%E2%80%98Who%E2%80%99s%20the%20cook%3F%20Him%20or%20I%3F%E2%80%99%20Sometimes%20he%20put%20more%20chilli%20to%20please%20the%20public%20who%20came%20to%20eat%20the%20paaya%2C%20but%20sometimes%20he%20did%20it%20to%20make%20Rahman%20miyan%20sick!%E2%80%9D%20Arshad%20snitched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20never%20forced%20him%20to%20eat%20the%20hot%20paaya.%20He%20himself%20liked%20to%20eat%20and%20then%20complain%20if%20he%20felt%20sick%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abrar%20said.%20%E2%80%9CAnyway%2C%20that%20day%20Arshad%20brought%20the%20chashni%20back%20just%20for%20fun.%20We%20warmed%20it%20and%20drank%20some%20of%20it%20ourselves.%20Rahman%20miyan%20was%20coughing%20and%20he%20wanted%20me%20to%20make%20him%20some%20kaarha%2C%20and%20he%20kept%20snapping%20at%20us%20for%20no%20reason.%20I%20put%20some%20cinnamon%2C%20pepper%2C%20ginger%20and%20tulsi%20leaves%20into%20the%20decoction%2C%20and%20then%20I%20also%20put%20some%20hot%20chashni.%20He%20liked%20it%20so%20much%20that%20he%20had%20three%20mugs%2C%20one%20after%20the%20other.%20Then%20he%20had%20a%20coughing%20fit%20but%20then%20he%20was%20fine.%20All%20this%20was%20before%2011%20o%E2%80%99clock.%20By%2011%20the%20customers%20had%20left%2C%20and%20we%20had%20cleaned%20up%20the%20place.%20That%20is%20why%20Shambhu%E2%80%99s%20chashni%20pateela%20was%20all%20washed%20and%20cleaned.%20We%20had%20put%20out%20the%20tandoor%20also%20and%20were%20just%20preparing%20to%20leave.%20I%20was%20sitting%20outside%20relaxing%20and%20Arshad%20was%20locking%20up%2C%20when%20Salman%20came%20to%20ask%20for%20work.%20Arshad%20made%20the%20mistake%20of%20taking%20him%20inside%20while%20Rahman%20miyan%20was%20counting%20money%2C%20and%20he%20became%20very%20upset%20and%20agitated.%20Then%20suddenly%20Rana%20sir%20arrived%20with%20Kanwal%20ji%20and%20we%20had%20to%20feed%20them.%20Rahman%20miyan%20made%20us%20light%20the%20tandoor%20fire%20again.%20Rana%20sir%20stayed%20for%20almost%20an%20hour%20and%20Kanwal%20ji%20and%20he%20said%20many%20things.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20things%3F%E2%80%9D%20ASI%20Achche%20Lal%20asked%20sharply%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRana%20sir%20said%20that%20serving%20nehari-roti%20was%20hurting%20Kanwal%E2%80%99s%20sentiments.%20Rahman%20miyan%20had%20become%20very%20tense%20and%20upset%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Arshad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CStress%20also%20causes%20onset%20of%20diabetic%20ketoacidosis.%20This%20kind%20of%20unwarranted%20bullying%20could%20also%20have%20been%20a%20factor%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jamal%2C%20while%20looking%20into%20the%20middle%20distance%20and%20away%20from%20Constable%20Rana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20have%20you%20not%20called%20Kanwal%20to%20this%20meeting%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Mrs%20Pushpa%20Kumari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKanwal%20ji%20is%20busy%20with%20Bulbhaddar%20babu%E2%80%99s%20bhandara%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shambhu%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20always%20suspected%20Kanwal%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mrs%20Pushpa%20Kumari%20to%20Aamna%20as%20an%20aside%20but%20in%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20Rana%20sir%20and%20Kanwal%20ji%20left%2C%20Rahman%20miyan%20told%20us%20to%20also%20leave%20quickly.%20He%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20let%20us%20put%20away%20the%20big%20pateela%20of%20qorma.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20Salman%20found%20it%20lying%20outside%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abrar%20further%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20had%20the%20chashni-kaarha%20himself.%20He%20wanted%20some%20home%20remedy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Arshad%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20you%E2%80%99ve%20been%20with%20him%20since%20childhood.%20Did%20you%20not%20know%20that%20his%20diabetes%20could%20cause%20a%20complication%3F%E2%80%9D%20Jamal%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDo%20even%20you%20know%2C%20Jamal%3F%E2%80%9D%20his%20father%20said.%20%E2%80%9CYou%E2%80%99re%20not%20very%20careful%20yourself.%20How%20would%20people%20near%20you%20know%20how%20risky%20something%20might%20be%3F%20Did%20you%20know%20Habib%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20had%20broken%20into%20smaller%20discussions.%20Laadley%20was%20making%20faces%20at%20Abrar%20and%20Arshad.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EKambakht%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20I%20had%20thought%20I%E2%80%99d%20keep%20you.%20But%20go%20rot%20in%20hell%2C%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%20was%20telling%20Habib%20that%20he%20had%20read%20about%20incidents%20when%20slaves%20rebelled%20through%20small%20acts%20of%20insubordination%2C%20by%20pretending%20to%20not%20hear%2C%20or%20spoiling%20their%20day%E2%80%99s%20work%2C%20and%20even%20getting%20whipped%20for%20it%20sometimes.%20Habib%20looked%20distracted%2C%20evidently%20wanting%20to%20return%20to%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETara%20was%20saying%20to%20Achche%20Lal%20that%20had%20the%20police%20done%20proper%20forensic%20tests%20of%20the%20pateelas%20and%20the%20plates%2C%20there%20would%20be%20more%20clarity%20about%20what%20was%20administered%20in%20what%20dosage%20and%20at%20what%20time.%20%E2%80%9CThen%20we%20would%20know%20if%20they%20had%20given%20him%20chashni%20to%20only%20tease%2C%20or%20to%20actually%20kill%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMadam%2C%20I%20can%20detain%20them%20and%20get%20a%20confession%20if%20you%20want%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Achche%20Lal%20tersely.%20Tara%20recoiled%20at%20the%20idea%3A%20%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20Achche%20Lal%20ji%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20not%20the%20way.%20You%20might%20beat%20a%20confession%20out%20of%20them%2C%20but%20we%20will%20still%20not%20know%20the%20truth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Pushpa%20Kumari%20also%20nodded%20in%20agreement.%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20they%20are%20lying%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EASI%20Achche%20Lal%20got%20up%20from%20his%20chair%20and%20signaled%20to%20Constable%20Rana%20to%20step%20out%20with%20him.%20%E2%80%9CSir%2C%20what%20should%20we%20do%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWell%20ACP%20saheb%20has%20closed%20the%20case.%20We%20can%20arrest%20them%20now%20and%20reopen%20the%20case%2C%20but%20we%20will%20first%20need%20his%20permission%2C%E2%80%9D%20Achche%20Lal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSir%2C%20there%20is%20nothing%20to%20go%20on.%20Even%20if%20we%20file%20a%20chargesheet%20they%E2%80%99ll%20get%20out%20immediately.%20Better%20to%20get%20them%20for%20something%20else%20next%20time.%20We%20can%20properly%20plan%20and%20put%20it%20on%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Constable%20Rana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhere%20are%20you%20learning%20all%20this%20Rana%3F%E2%80%9D%20said%20Achche%20Lal%20with%20obvious%20distaste.%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20involve%20them%20now%20because%20this%20case%20is%20complicated.%20Really%2C%20someone%20can%20argue%20that%20stress%20was%20a%20contributing%20factor%20also.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSir%2C%20you%20mustn%E2%80%99t%20believe%20what%20they%20are%20saying.%20They%20are%20liars%3B%20always%20trying%20to%20implicate%20the%20police.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20policemen%20returned%2C%20Abrar%20and%20Arshad%20had%20slinked%20into%20a%20corner%20and%20looked%20suitably%20fearful.%20It%20appeared%20that%20Laadley%20had%20just%20hit%20them.%20He%20was%20being%20pulled%20away%20from%20them%20by%20Jamal%2C%20while%20Zaitoon%20nani%20was%20now%20speaking%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCase%20is%20closed%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20ASI%20Achche%20Lal%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20if%20I%20hear%20of%20anything%20in%20the%20future%2C%20any%20crime%20in%20the%20area%2C%20I%E2%80%99ll%20come%20and%20find%20you.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20lay%20eyes%20on%20you%20for%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20you%20understand%3F%20You%20get%20out%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20silence%20for%20a%20moment%20and%20then%20Laadley%20sighed%20loudly.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20best%20it%20was%20a%20contributory%20factor.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20they%20gave%20it%20to%20him%20intentionally.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThen%20what%20did%20you%20just%20hit%20them%20for%3F%E2%80%9D%20Jamal%20exclaimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%20shrugged%3A%20%E2%80%9CEven%20giving%20Rahman%20miyan%20chashni%20in%20the%20kaarha%20was%20wrong.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20probably%20gave%20him%20the%20chashni%20much%20earlier%20in%20the%20evening.%20And%20he%20carried%20on%20through%20the%20evening%2C%20so%20they%20must%20not%20have%20realised%20how%20ill%20he%20would%20become%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20boy%20from%20the%20madarsa%20spoke%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20they%20must%20have%20finished%20the%20chashni%20much%20earlier%20in%20the%20evening.%20That%20is%20how%20my%20pateela%20was%20washed%2C%20whereas%20the%20big%20qorma%20pateela%20from%20which%20Rana%20sir%20was%20served%20was%20left%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shambhu%20also%20agreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnyway%20they%20will%20suffer%20for%20their%20deed.%20Nobody%20will%20speak%20to%20them%2C%20or%20give%20them%20any%20work.%20Total%20boycott%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Laadley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHmmnh%2C%20they%20will%20be%20back%20in%20a%20day%20begging%20and%20pleading%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jamal%20with%20a%20laugh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20the%20group%20started%20to%20break.%20People%20got%20up%20to%20leave.%20The%20man%20in%20the%20sleeveless%20brown%20sweater%20and%20checked%20lungi%20crept%20upon%20Laadley%20and%20whispered%20in%20his%20ear%2C%20%E2%80%9CAm%20I%20to%20serve%20kababs%20or%20not%3F%20Nobody%20has%20been%20declared%20murderer.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSwine!%20Is%20this%20the%20time%3F%E2%80%9D%20Laadley%20thundered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20end.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ENote%20from%20the%20author%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20murder%20mystery%2C%20such%20as%20it%20is%2C%20is%20done.%20Thank%20you%20Seema%20Chishti%20for%20inviting%20me%20to%20write.%20It%20was%20a%20wonderful%20experience.%20I%20should%20have%20written%20the%20whole%20story%20and%20then%20broken%20it%20up%20into%20parts%2C%20for%20serialised%20publication.%20Instead%20I%20wrote%20from%20week%20to%20week%2C%20issuing%20two%20chapters%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20was%20exciting%2C%20interactive%20and%20alive.%20But%20I%20never%20submitted%20on%20time%2C%20thus%20eating%20into%20my%20editor%20Jahnavi%20Sen%E2%80%99s%20weekends.%20Thank%20you%2C%20Jahnavi%2C%20for%20your%20patience%2C%20and%20for%20your%20technical%20team%E2%80%99s%20time.%20Thank%20you%20for%20the%20silent%20encouragement%2C%20tempered%20often%20with%20silent%20disapproval%20at%20the%20late%20submissions.%20Both%20were%20helpful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20I%20had%20at%20least%20some%20readers%20who%20actually%20waited%20for%20the%20next%20installment%3A%20my%20parents%2C%20Paro%2C%20my%20muanijaan%2C%20and%20my%20friends%20Mayukhi%2C%20Kaiser%2C%20Monty%2C%20Mallika%2C%20Sujata%20and%20Richa.%20I%E2%80%99m%20most%20indebted.%20My%20sisters%20did%20not%20wait%20for%20the%20installments%2C%20and%20only%20read%20chapters%20under%20duress%3B%20then%20they%20offered%20their%20criticism.%20It%20was%20very%20useful%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20also%20to%20Vanita%2C%20Veena%20and%20Anjolie%20for%20their%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20very%20special%20thanks%20to%20Dr%20Sumit%20Ray%2C%20for%20making%20time%20to%20help%20me%20resolve%20the%20murder.%20I%20had%20started%20to%20write%20without%20an%20end%20in%20mind%2C%20and%20made%20mistakes%20along%20the%20way%3A%20he%20helped%20me%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98means%E2%80%99%20question%2C%20so%20central%20to%20a%20murder%20mystery%2C%20and%20with%20tying%20all%20the%20loose%20ends%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThank%20you%20Paro%2C%20Abbu%20and%20Mama%20for%20reading%20and%20editing%20and%20debating%20the%20plot%20points%20with%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706357158000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F27150726%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-26-at-3.41.10-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffiction%2Fa-mood-for-murder-episode-10-saunf%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Wire%20WhoDunnIt%3A%20This%20is%20the%20final%20part%20of%20a%20serialised%20detective%20story%20by%20Shahrukh%20Alam.%20It%20is%20a%20work%20of%20fiction.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffiction%2Fa-mood-for-murder-episode-10-saunf%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Modi's%20Drifting%20Flagship%20Schemes%20and%20Failed%20Guarantees%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30194902%2FEffect-49.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20reports%20about%20the%20deployment%20of%201%2C500%20specially%20equipped%20vehicles%20to%20cover%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%202.5%20lakh%20panchayats%20first%20appeared%2C%20it%20was%20officially%20called%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fviksitbharatsankalp.gov.in%2F%5C%22%3EViksit%20Bharat%20Sankalp%20Yatra%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98.%20Supervised%20by%20senior%20officers%20and%20equipped%20with%20GPS%20and%20drone