se%20%E2%80%98Modi%E2%80%99s%20guarantee%E2%80%99%2018%20times%20in%20a%2019-minute%20speech.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20knows%20how%20many%20schemes%20he%20has%20announced%20in%20the%20past%2010%20years.%20This%20writer%20counted%20142%20recorded%20schemes.%20An%20official%20list%20cites%2040%20schemes%20with%20duly%20approved%20logos%20which%20were%20announced%20in%202015%20and%202016.%20There%20are%20at%20least%2020%20schemes%20with%20%E2%80%98PM%E2%80%99%20prefixes%20(the%20list)%2C%20like%20PM%20Kisan%20and%20PM%20Awas%20Yojana.%20Then%20there%20are%20schemes%20starting%20with%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98Amrit%E2%80%99%20(Amrit%20Kaal%2C%20Amrit%20Bharat%20Trains)%2C%20a%20favourite%20term%20for%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGhosts%20of%20failed%20schemes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20formal%20evaluation%20of%20the%20Modi%20schemes%20has%20been%20made%20nor%20are%20any%20authentic%20figures%20available.%20Most%20are%20flippant%20claims%20made%20by%20the%20PM%20or%20his%20ministers%20aimed%20at%20boosting%20the%20image.%20From%202017-18%2C%20the%20mainstream%20media%20has%20ceased%20carrying%20critical%20reports.%20The%20real-time%20implementation%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98guarantee%E2%80%99%20has%20never%20been%20subjected%20to%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fthe-many-economic-guarantees-and-promises-of-the-modi-government%5C%22%3EThe%20Many%20Economic%20Guarantees%20and%20Promises%20of%20the%20Modi%20Government%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20the%20case%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20guarantee%20on%20Ganga%20cleaning.%20Renamed%20Namami%20Gange%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethe%20project%20was%20announced%20in%20May%202014%20as%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Clife%E2%80%99s%20mission%E2%80%9D.%20As%20per%20a%202021%20report%2C%20only%2020%25%20of%20the%20sewerage%20plant%20of%20the%20Rs%2020%2C000%20crore%20scheme%20was%20completed.%20The%20National%20Mission%20for%20Clean%20Ganga%20expects%20to%20add%207%2C000%20million%20litres%20of%20sewage%20by%202026.%20This%20is%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20PM%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fseven-years-down-cleaning-the-ganga-remains-a-work-in-progress%2Farticle67259400.ece%5C%22%3Elife%E2%80%99s%20mission%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20after%2010%20years%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELook%20at%20another%20Modi%20guarantee%20%E2%80%94%20100%20new%20smart%20cities%20%E2%80%94%20announced%20in%20June%202015.%20By%20mid-2015%2C%2014%20countries%2C%20including%20the%20United%20States%2C%20France%2C%20and%20China%2C%20lined%20up%20to%20grab%20lucrative%20contracts%20for%20the%20Rs%204%20lakh%20crore%20pie.%20France%E2%80%99s%20Thales%20and%20the%20US-based%20IBM%20and%20Cisco%20Systems%20began%20consultations%20for%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%2018%20million-dollar%20digital%20market.%20Prospects%20of%20land%20at%20cheap%20rates%20were%20additional%20attractions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Bank%2C%20Asian%20Development%20Bank%20(ADB)%2C%20and%20United%20States%20Agency%20for%20International%20Development%20(USAID)%20offered%20loans%20for%20the%20project.%20Financial%20dailies%20reported%20PwC%2C%20McKinsey%2C%20Lea%20Associates%2C%20and%20Bosch%20were%20to%20be%20the%20empaneled%20as%20consultants.%20But%20then%20there%20was%20a%20sudden%20silence.%20And%20the%20dream%20city%20project%20became%20just%20another%20scheme%20to%20modernise%20small%20bits%20and%20pieces%20of%20existing%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20pre-election%20guarantee%20to%20remit%20Rs%2015%20lakhs%20in%20every%20Indian%E2%80%99s%20bank%20account%20is%20rather%20curious.%20This%20led%20to%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20making%20contradictory%20statements.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20original%20remarks%20at%20an%20election%20rally%20in%20Kanker%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20were%20denied%20six%20years%20later%20by%20defence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27145721%2F404088963_1118521242975440_6389008391481424915_n-2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27145721%2F404088963_1118521242975440_6389008391481424915_n-2.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27145721%2F404088963_1118521242975440_6389008391481424915_n-2-300x141.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27145721%2F404088963_1118521242975440_6389008391481424915_n-2-1024x480.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686558%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22563%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20group%20of%20women%20hold%20a%20poster%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20at%20an%20election%20rally%20in%20Rajasthan.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2Fnarendramodi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20his%20cabinet%20college%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20said%20Modi%20made%20the%20guarantee%20because%20they%20were%20not%20expecting%20to%20win%20the%20election.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20we%20must%20just%20laugh%20and%20move%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gadkari%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fnitin-gadkari-reveals-why-pm-narendra-modi-vowed-to-put-15-lakh-in-your-account%2Farticleshow%2F66141101.cms%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20most%20authentic%20voice%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.economictimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fpm-modis-promise-of-rs-15-lakh-in-each-account-an-idiom-amit-shah%2Farticleshow%2F46139139.cms%5C%22%3Econfirmed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20guarantee%20but%20said%20it%20was%20just%20an%20%E2%80%98idiom%E2%80%99%20(%3Cem%3Ejumla%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%2C%20however%2C%20had%20treated%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ejumla%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20as%20a%20genuine%20guarantee%20and%20rushed%20in%20large%20numbers%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Ftrends%2Fpm-modis-promise-of-rs-15-lakh-for-everyone-rumours-make-people-rush-to-open-accounts-4277271.html%5C%22%3Eopen%20new%20bank%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20become%20%3Cem%3Elabharthis%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELook%20how%20the%20ghosts%20of%20failed%20schemes%20haunt%20the%20graveyard%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20forgotten%20guarantees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EModi%20announced%20the%20Mumbai-Ahmedabad%20bullet%20train%20project%20in%20September%202014%20with%20big%20fanfare.%20Bhumipujan%20was%20held%20on%20September%2014%2C%202017%2C%20and%20after%20frequently%20shifting%20goalposts%2C%20the%20target%20for%20completion%20was%20fixed%20for%20August%2015%2C%202022.%20But%2C%20as%20per%20the%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesnownews.com%2Fmumbai%2Findias-first-bullet-train-project-misses-deadline-vapi-sabarmati-section-likely-to-get-launch-in-august-2027-article-101303721%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20new%20deadline%20for%20the%20Vapi-Sabarmati%20section%20is%202027.%20That%20will%20make%20it%2013%C2%A0%20years%E2%80%99%20delay.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20project%20cost%20has%20almost%20doubled%20from%20Rs%201.08%20lakh%20crore%20to%20Rs%202%20lakh%20crore.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20April%202017%2C%20Modi%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-elections%2Fmaharashtra%2Fnews%2Fwill-double-farmers-income-by-2022-says-modi%2Farticleshow%2F68712669.cms%3Futm_source%3Dsubstack%26utm_medium%3Demail%5C%22%3Eanother%20guarantee%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20to%20double%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income%20by%202022.%20Six%20years%20later%2C%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20ta