aled%20by%20a%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20question%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fone-in-four-ujjwala-yojana-beneficiaries-took-zero-or-one-lpg-cylinder-refil%5C%22%3Eshowed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20of%20the%209.58%20crore%20PMUY%20households%2C%201.8%20crore%20bought%20no%20refills%20while%20another%201.51%20cr%20bought%20just%20one%20refill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20due%20to%20the%20hefty%20hike%20in%20prices%20of%20cylinders.%20Parliament%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsclick.in%2FMP-LPG-Hikes-Gas-Out-Ujjwala-Cardholders-Only-30%2525-Active-Refills-Drop-3-Cylinders-Year%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%2013%2C000%20%3Cem%3Elabharthis%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20never%20refilled%20after%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyushman%20Bharat%2C%20another%20showpiece%20of%20Modi%20guarantee%2C%20is%20riddled%20with%20fraudulent%20transactions%2C%20invalid%20names%2C%20duplicate%20PMJDY%20IDs%2C%20and%20unrealistic%20date%20of%20birth%20and%20size%20of%20a%20family%20in%20a%20household%2C%20The%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20(CAG)%20also%20revealed%20large-scale%20payments%20to%20dead%20patients.%20For%20revealing%20such%20irregularities%2C%20the%20national%20auditor%20was%20castigated%20and%20concerned%20officials%20were%20punished%20with%20transfers%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%20July%202015%2C%20Skill%20India%20had%20raised%20much%20hope%20among%20the%20aspiring%20youth.%20However%2C%20from%20the%20beginning%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fwhy-i-cant-find-a-good-plumber-exploring-the-skill-india-mess%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20scheme%20was%20plagued%20by%20wrong%20selection%20of%20courses%2C%20outdated%20technological%20level%2C%20and%20fraudulent%20reporting%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Investigation%20by%20another%20daily%20found%20a%20majority%20of%20institutes%20that%20provided%20training%20t