a%20member%20of%20the%20Jharkhand%20Animal%20Welfare%20Society%2C%20he%20also%20developed%20over%2050%20wheelchairs%20for%20injured%20or%20paralysed%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20family%20practised%20carpentry%20till%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20adept%20at%20tools%20and%20electrical%20design%20due%20to%20my%20course%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20found%20the%20harmful%20effects%20of%20air%20fresheners%20and%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20anything%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323755%2Fmothers-anupama-charulatha-swmrt-bengaluru-plastic-free-low-waste-wedding-composting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etruly%20eco-friendly%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20his%20passion%20for%20creation%20pushed%20him%20to%20build%20one%20using%20natural%20ingredients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20poisonous%20chemicals%20in%20air%20fresheners.%20All%20you%20need%20to%20do%20is%20read%20the%20ingredient%20list%20behind%20any%20air%20freshener.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20safe%20for%20children%20(mentioned%20in%20the%20packaging)%20and%20animals%20to%20inhale.%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20a%20freshener%20which%20was%20safe%20for%20the%20environment%20as%20well%20as%20humans%20and%20animals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20Rajiv%20focused%20on%20creating%20natural%20fragrances%20using%20flower%20waste.%20He%20collected%20jasmine%20and%20roses%20from%20a%20nearby%20temple%2C%20air-dried%20the%20petals%2C%20ground%20them%20into%20powder%20using%20a%20mixer%2C%20and%20combined%20them%20with%20coconut%20husk%20waste.%20After%20allowing%20the%20mixture%20to%20air%20dry%20for%20a%20few%20days%2C%20the%20fragrance%20was%20prepared.%20Rajiv%20then%20placed%20this%20fragrance%20into%20a%20glass%20bottle%20and%20crafted%20an%20outer%20cover%20using%20wood%2C%20resulting%20in%20his%20homemade%2C%20eco-friendly%20fragrance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC2P9fEGofLa%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC2P9fEGofLa%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC2P9fEGofLa%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20ALVE%20GREEN%20SOLUTIONS%20(%40alveindia)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20it%20may%20seem%20straightforward%2C%20creating%20the%20final%20product%20involved%20numerous%20trials%20and%20combinations%20for%20Rajiv.%20With%20support%20from%20his%20mother%2C%20who%20is%20the%20co-founder%20of%20ALVE%20Green%20Solutions%2C%20he%20worked%20diligently%20for%20over%20eight%20months.%20It%20took%20more%20than%2020%20prototypes%20before%20achieving%20the%20ideal%20result%2C%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20my%20professors%20saw%20this%2C%20they%20were%20amazed.%20They%20said%20that%20this%20needs%20to%20be%20given%20to%20a%20bigger%20audience%20and%20is%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour.%20They%20helped%20me%20perfect%20it%20with%20the%20help%20of%20machines%20in%20the%20college%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Rajiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20smart%2C%20zero-plastic%20air%20freshener%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1706154602428-min-1706189932.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22alve%20air%20fresheners%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1706154602428-min-1706189932.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1706154602428-min-1706189932-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1706154602428-min-1706189932-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1706154602428-min-1706189932-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1706154602428-min-1706189932-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1706154602428-min-1706189932-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-339845%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThese%20air%20fresheners%20are%20eco-friendly%2C%20smart%20and%20made%20of%20floral%20waste%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20freshener%20is%20available%20in%20three%20variants%20for%20homes%2C%20offices%2C%20and%20cars%2C%20offering%20a%20choice%20of%2015%20fragrances.%20Each%20unit%20is%20equipped%20with%20smart%20sensors%20that%20automatically%20activate%20and%20deactivate%20based%20on%20the%20detection%20of%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20presence.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20is%20compatible%20with%20Google%20Assistant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20freshener%20features%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Ftopics%2Fsustainability%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiodegradable%20body%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20can%20be%20composted%20after%20use%2C%20and%20its%20refills%20are%20organic%20%E2%80%94%20crafted%20from%20temple%20flower%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20nature%E2%80%99s%20intelligence%20in%20retaining%20the%20fragrances.%20Chemical%20fresheners%20use%20LPG%20to%20retain%20the%20fragrance.%20We%20use%20natural%20ingredients%20for%20that%20with%20no%20chemicals.%20We%20do%20not%20use%20any%20heat%2C%20water%20vapour%20or%20chemicals%20to%20diffuse%20our%20fragrances.%20We%20use%20our%20own%20Air%20Diffusion%20Technology%20with%20sensors%20to%20diffuse%20aroma%20evenly%20in%20the%20surroundings%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20designer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajiv%20has%20partnered%20with%20more%20than%2030%20temples%20in%20Jamshedpur%20to%20obtain%20floral%20waste.%20Every%20day%2C%20he%20collects%20a%20minimum%20of%203%20kg%20of%20floral%20waste%20from%20each%20temple.%20To%20date%2C%20he%20has%20recycled%201%2C500%20kg%20of%20temple%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20noteworthy%20aspect%20is%20that%20this%20freshener%20is%20safe%20for%20animals%20also.%20Working%20in%20the%20Jharkhand%20Animal%20Welfare%20Society%20since%202018%2C%20Rajiv%20was%20shocked%20by%20the%20effects%20of%20human%20behaviour%20on%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rajiv%20made%20wheelchairs%20for%20dogs%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156-300x171.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156-500x285.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156-768x438.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156-1536x876.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156-150x86.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-339849%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22913%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERajiv%20made%20%E2%80%98wheelchairs%E2%80%99%20for%20dogs%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20to%20rescue%20cows%20and%20bulls.%20When%20they%20were%20operated%20upon%2C%20veterinarians%20found%20plastic%20in%20their%20stomachs%2C%20which%20they%20were%20not%20able%20to%20digest.%20I%20have%20been%20against%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Fauthor%2Fsowmyamani%2Fpage%2F3%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplastic%20use%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20that%20day.%20Our%20fresheners%20too%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20plastic%20in%20them.%20Just%20put%20our%20device%20in%20your%20garden%20after%20use%20and%20it%20will%20get%20composted%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERunning%20the%20startup%20from%20his%20home%20currently%2C%20Rajiv%20hopes%20to%20expand%20soon.%20ALVE%20Green%20Solutions%20has%20collaborated%20with%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%20Bangalore%2C%20where%20five%20college%20students%20will%20be%20working%20with%20the%20startup%20to%20develop%20the%20product.%20The%20air%20fresheners%20are%20currently%20being%20sold%20offline%2C%20at%20events%2C%20and%20through%20their%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CALVE%20is%20derived%20from%20the%20word%20Alveoli%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tiny%20sac-like%20structure%20present%20in%20our%20lungs%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20exchange%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20and%20oxygen.%20Without%20this%20organ%2C%20the%20body%20fails%20to%20survive%2C%20thus%20making%20it%20a%20most%20important%20part%20of%20our%20body%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Rajiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20he%20explains%20that%20he%20wants%20ALVE%20to%20be%20an%20important%20part%20of%20each%20home%20for%20healthier%20living.%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20create%20products%20that%20not%20only%20meet%20human%20needs%20but%20also%20leave%20a%20positive%20imprint%20on%20our%20planet.%20Our%20vision%20at%20ALVE%20is%20to%20inspire%20a%20world%20where%20fresh%2C%20clean%20air%20is%20not%20a%20luxury%20but%20a%20sustainable%20standard%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706192933000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D339831%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Looking%20for%20ecofriendly%20air%20fresheners%3F%20Jamshedpur's%20Rajiv%20Sharma%20innovated%20ALVE%20smart%20air%20fresheners%20by%20recycling%201500%20kgs%20of%20temple%20flower%20waste.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339831%2Fjamshedpur-rajiv-sharma-alve-smart-air-fresheners-plastic-free-eco-friendly-temple-flower-waste%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%23GiftaSchoolKit%3A%20This%20Republic%20Day%2C%20Change%20a%20Child%E2%80%99s%20Future%20By%20Donating%20Just%20Rs%20500%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELife%20isn%E2%80%99t%20easy%20for%20Vikas%20(%3Cem%3Ename%20changed%3C%2Fem%3E)%20a%20Class%202%20student%20of%20the%20Zilla%20Parishad%20school%20in%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Aaregaon%20village.%20His%20father%2C%20a%20farm%20labourer%2C%20earns%20an%20average%20of%20Rs%20150%20a%20day%2C%20a%20meagre%20amount%20that%2