g%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDev-Raturi-4-1705931014-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDev-Raturi-4-1705931014-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDev-Raturi-4-1705931014-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDev-Raturi-4-1705931014-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338749%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDev%E2%80%99s%20inspirational%20journey%20is%20taught%20in%20the%20schools%20of%20China%20today.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDev%20also%20demonstrated%20the%20importance%20of%20cross-cultural%20communication.%20He%20not%20only%20brought%20Indian%20food%20culture%20to%20China%20but%20also%20spread%20Chinese%20culture%20to%20India%20through%20films%20and%20other%20means.%20This%20kind%20of%20cross-cultural%20exchange%20helps%20to%20improve%20the%20understanding%20and%20friendship%20between%20different%20nationalities%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20an%20Indian%2C%20Dev%20did%20not%20forget%20his%20roots%20after%20tasting%20success%20in%20China.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20he%20has%20brought%20Indian%20culture%20to%20China%20so%20that%20more%20people%20can%20understand%20and%20recognise%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20I%20employ%20nearly%20100%20people%20including%20Chinese%20and%20Indian%20workers.%20And%2030%20percent%20of%20the%20money%20I%20make%20goes%20to%20charity%2C%20either%20in%20India%20or%20China%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Dev.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20an%20honour%20for%20me%20that%20my%20life%20journey%20is%20being%20taught%20in%20Class%207%20in%20schools%20of%20Xi%E2%80%99an%2C%20where%20I%20started%20my%20entrepreneurship%20journey.%20Although%20I%E2%80%99m%20neither%20a%20gradu