-set-up-eco-friendly-homestay-in-nilgiris-jungle-hut-harvests-solar-power%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econstructing%20the%20greywater%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20takes%20the%20wastewater%2C%20filters%20it%2C%20and%20channels%20it%20into%20the%20garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20always%20took%20his%20advice%20seriously%2C%E2%80%9D%20Luv%20says.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20the%20last%20batch%20of%20people%20trained%20by%20the%20British%20and%20joined%20the%20Indian%20Forest%20Institute%20in%20Coimbatore%20in%201945.%20He%20was%20among%20the%20first%20trained%20people%20who%20joined%20the%20Government%20of%20Rajasthan%20Forest%20Department%20in%20the%20capacity%20of%20a%20ranger%20and%20helped%20set%20up%20Ranthambore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELuv%20recalls%20the%20day%20his%20grandfather%20was%20on%20site%20and%20Luv%20was%20planning%20to%20clear%20out%20the%20garden%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwell-manicured%20lawn%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20shared%20a%20lesson%20with%20me%20that%20I%20still%20follow.%20He%20told%20me%20to%20look%20for%20dry%20leaves%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20ground.%20These%2C%20he%20said%2C%20were%20indicators%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332749%2Fex-banker-sunando-sen-built-tanhau-sustainable-himalayan-homestay-corbett-restore-wildlife%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthy%20ecosystem%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20Luv%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Utsav%20Camp%20is%20a%20sustainable%20oasis%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20powered%20by%20solar%20panels%20and%20following%20a%20stringent%20zero-mile%20approach%20to%20source%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuests%20are%20promised%20a%20holistic%20wildlife%20experience.%20To%20this%20end%2C%20loud%20music%2C%20partying%2C%20etc%2C%20is%20prohibited.%20While%20Luv%20enjoys%20thrilling%20his%20guests%20with%20tales%20and%20information%20about%20the%20species%20observed%20on%20a%20safari